Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.30,0:01:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect to be first.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.86,0:01:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Other than getting one's affairs in order and simplifying life, for people who are increasingly
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.94,0:01:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,experiencing non-dual reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.38,0:01:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're increasingly experiencing what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.35,0:01:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-dual reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.35,0:01:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.35,0:01:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.35,0:01:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-dual, non-duality.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.35,0:01:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-duality.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.54,0:01:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.54,0:01:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.54,0:01:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore find relationships and work and life structures as you previously knew
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.10,0:01:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,it relatively irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.64,0:01:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Less attractive, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.70,0:01:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What guidance can you provide?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.91,0:02:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The motivation has to shift from gain, huh, and the various things that ordinarily
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.63,0:02:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,steer people through the linear world, and in their place to take on the value of non-linear
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.81,0:02:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,values, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.81,0:02:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, to be of service to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.34,0:02:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So you may hold the job out of gain, out of vanity for the title, out of desire, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.64,0:02:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you transcend that level.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, of what meaning or significance is the same job.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.36,0:02:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It may transform in meaning, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.36,0:02:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Did that answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.04,0:02:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, you're serving a function for humanity and society, and that becomes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.51,0:02:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the way you contextualize what you do, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.13,0:02:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,To be of service, then, no matter what you do, is really a being of service to life,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.87,0:03:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, in all of its expressions and forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.87,0:03:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes 20 workmen to lift a tent for the circus, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.83,0:03:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.83,0:03:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All in general, it has to do with Alzheimer's and that condition, and one has the experience
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,that I've had a couple of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.83,0:03:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.83,0:03:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The Alzheimer's is a very good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.83,0:03:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.83,0:03:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, patients that have Alzheimer's.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.17,0:03:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Alzheimer's, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.17,0:03:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Alzheimer's, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.17,0:03:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I never can say that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.17,0:03:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got a Z, a Z in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.17,0:03:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, a Z.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.17,0:03:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.17,0:03:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.17,0:03:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.17,0:03:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell them what is really happening with the soul, with people who have that disease?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.17,0:03:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell who's happening with whose soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.55,0:03:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yours or the patient's?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.55,0:03:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the patient's.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.55,0:03:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The patient's.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.55,0:03:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the patient's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.55,0:03:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.55,0:03:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what's happening with the patient's soul is up to the patient and God.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you want to know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she must know they're in pain, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I was the only doctor in the county, and they would go to the nursing home and
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,see the Alzheimer's patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I saw them all over the county, from Prescott on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still a lot of back talk in the background.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I found that most of it, that the anguish was on the part of the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.80,0:04:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The patient, I'd go to see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They'd say, oh, poor Aunt Granny.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't remember who she is anymore, and this and that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And the family is all upset and wailing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'd go see Aunt Granny.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say, how are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.96,0:04:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.96,0:04:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.96,0:04:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.96,0:04:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.96,0:04:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How's the food?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.96,0:04:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.96,0:04:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You got any complaints today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.96,0:04:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.14,0:05:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what day it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.14,0:05:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.43,0:05:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how old you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She said, oh, I'm a lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, she doesn't remember how old she is, and who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.59,0:05:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the subjective experiential of straightforward Alzheimer's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There's senility, dimension, whatever you want to call it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The main anguish is in the witness, because if you don't remember a lot of what went on,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.52,0:05:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,what difference does it make?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,As it is, most people don't remember what went on in their life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you give me a minute-by-minute, second-by-second recall, you know, of even one day in your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.25,0:05:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.25,0:05:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You can remember a few highlights.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.25,0:05:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what people mourn is really the vanity of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the vanity of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.38,0:05:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember I saw my grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.18,0:06:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She was 99.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And I went to see her, and she says, oh, you're from New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.94,0:06:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.94,0:06:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, my grandson is a doctor in New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, well, yes, Granny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I began to talk about who I was and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And all of a sudden, she said, all of a sudden, she started to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.10,0:06:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So, would you say there's no difference, then, between a gastrointestinal trance disorder or Alzheimer's?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Straight Alzheimer's.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.10,0:06:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, then there's Alzheimer's would disturb the emotionality and all, but that's irrelevant to the Alzheimer's,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.10,0:06:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,because lots of people at the same age without Alzheimer's get the same thing, depression or agitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.10,0:06:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you treat the negative symptoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:07:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But Alzheimer's itself, I always felt as though the spirit has already left the body progressively, and there's very little left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know, Bill Wilson, who was the founder of AA, and I knew him for years before he died, and I was one of the doctors who used to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And he would lapse periodically.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And he would say, he visited different realms of heaven, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He would go into it like a lapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And he would say, it is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.20,0:07:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many mansions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many mansions on my father's side, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that there is, what he was saying, which we recently discovered with kinesiology, is that there are multiple heavens, multiple ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, as a clinician, in dealing with Alzheimer's, what is your recommendation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.41,0:07:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure they have breakfast and lunch and dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.41,0:07:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:08:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Got enough socks for the week, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're bringing in books from another line here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.17,0:08:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That answers the mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll just sign in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.17,0:08:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.17,0:08:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Personal inscriptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.17,0:08:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I can do to get him to sign his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.36,0:08:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.36,0:08:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I did put it with best regards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.36,0:08:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.36,0:08:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.36,0:08:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He usually doesn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.36,0:08:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.36,0:08:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,On the one hand, one wants to serve the higher good without considering gain and loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But, on the other hand, one wants to live in abundance rather than in poverty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you reconcile those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you got against poverty?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.84,0:08:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it just feels nicer to have, you know, a credit card, be able to take an airplane.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.84,0:08:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not poverty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's lack of wealth, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Poverty is something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Lack of wealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.07,0:08:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's a very common problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.26,0:08:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably one of the most common problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.26,0:08:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.26,0:08:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.26,0:08:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.26,0:08:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.26,0:08:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.26,0:08:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.58,0:08:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.58,0:08:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.58,0:08:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.58,0:08:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:08:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.19,0:09:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.19,0:09:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.19,0:09:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.19,0:09:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.19,0:09:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.32,0:09:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's probably the most common.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You become, you fulfill your own potential to the greatest degree you can fulfill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And the consequences are automatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing you need to do to make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.99,0:09:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, because of the consequence of that which you are, you draw to yourself by attraction
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.02,0:09:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that which will elude you if you seek it out of.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.18,0:09:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.40,0:09:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The negativity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.40,0:09:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, one should learn to enjoy what the world would call poverty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.17,0:10:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The simplicity of it, the lack of demand of it, I mean what you need in the refrigerator
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.04,0:10:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is a six pack of Pepsi and a piece of cheese, what else do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.92,0:10:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I lived that way for years, and in those days I used to truck manure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.24,0:10:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,When I left the world, I left a grand lifestyle, more grand than you can even imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean it was grand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.89,0:10:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The club I belonged to was so exclusive, nobody knows the name of it to this day, but they
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,were the heads of all the great sources of wealth in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.13,0:10:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I just put my tools in the back of the truck and drove away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.80,0:10:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It was great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Free as a bird, free, free.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.15,0:11:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to drive down the highway with a load of manure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it for ten bucks, so they're the big dairy farm in McGuireville, and for ten bucks
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,they'd load up the back of the truck and I would truck it all the way to Sedona.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.34,0:11:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the manure baron of Sedona.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.08,0:11:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I controlled the market.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.12,0:11:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody wanted to get their truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.12,0:11:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick up ten bucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.42,0:11:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Truck 30 with manure, so anyway, so I would sell it for 40 or 45, so I bought it for ten,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.43,0:11:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,sold it for 45, and to do that I only had to drive eight miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.33,0:11:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you can't beat that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was free as a bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.55,0:11:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I could do it when I wanted to do it, not do it when I wanted to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.35,0:11:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If I didn't need money, heck with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.55,0:11:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.13,0:11:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I lived that way for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.05,0:11:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Only reluctantly was forced to give it up, to tell you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.64,0:11:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.64,0:12:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you enjoy simplicity, so don't see it as poverty, see it as simplicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.64,0:12:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And this period of simplicity is a gift, and when you've extracted all there is to learn
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,from that, that learning phase goes over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.86,0:12:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You may then have to learn how to be the responsible steward of abundance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be sorry you weren't the poor again, I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.18,0:12:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.18,0:12:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, I'm Grant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Grant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.41,0:12:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.91,0:12:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is John.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm honored and also a little bit intimidated being up here, so if my question doesn't make
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.91,0:12:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,any sense, just re-ask it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.91,0:12:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have to make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.91,0:12:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.91,0:12:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What you said earlier this morning about meditation, my spiritual ego felt a little
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.67,0:12:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,disparaged by that, an avid practicer of meditation myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And then with further reflection, what I got from what you said was that if all you did
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:12:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,was meditate, then that would mean nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If it didn't translate in some change of behavior, some way of perceiving things, responding to
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.54,0:13:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,things, then it would mean nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And in my sense of it is that it has helped me create a sense of equanimity about the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.08,0:13:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,coming and going of things, processes in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.08,0:13:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So I myself have found it very beneficial.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.08,0:13:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it for 20 years, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.08,0:13:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.08,0:13:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the second part of my question was...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So it wasn't exactly a fizzle, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.08,0:13:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,In your comments about it, it was somewhat negativistic about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I was wondering, did I perceive what you said upon further reflection to be more
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.11,0:13:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,accurate of what you were trying to say, to how would you say that the 20 years of meditating
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.40,0:13:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,two hours a day, did that have anything to do with how you are now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be hard to say, because you see, it's the intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:14:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The intention with which you meditate, pray, walk the maze, asceticism, I also did asceticism,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.62,0:14:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and left my own devices, I'd weigh about 90, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So asceticism can become a way of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.51,0:14:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Certain things are realized, I'm certain, as a result of the meditative state itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.51,0:14:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm saying is how well does it transpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.51,0:14:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You meditate for an hour and you gain some interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.51,0:14:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You have interesting insights.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.69,0:14:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, to me, it gives me practice at being in the audience looking at the movie, as opposed
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,to the actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes you into the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.18,0:14:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.18,0:14:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So now, what you want to do, maybe I didn't make it clear, is translate what you saw from
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,meditation into contemplation so it becomes what you are in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:14:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.18,0:14:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So I think that kind of augments that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.18,0:14:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sort of a laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.18,0:15:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, also meditation trains you in one-pointedness of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.18,0:15:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And that one-pointedness of mind later comes on usefully in other spiritual practices.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Because when you decide to make what I call the final run, when you decide to make the
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.27,0:15:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,final run, you're going to be walking the edge of the razor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to walk the edge of the razor and stay on the edge of the razor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.62,0:15:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And you need that disciplined one-pointedness of mind to see the crest of each experience
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.62,0:15:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,arising and to release it as it arises.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.62,0:15:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And not to anticipate jumping to the front of the wave of experience, which is control
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and also fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Nor is it hanging to the back of the wave, which is clinging to the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.62,0:15:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So to be on the wave of the presence of now is an expertise that can be learned in meditation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.62,0:15:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.62,0:15:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Then applied in the style of contemplation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.17,0:16:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So contemplation is a way of being meditative about life and the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.58,0:16:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,About life as you walk through life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's only an artificial disparity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.42,0:16:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What I was trying to point out is a lot of times people isolate that, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.42,0:16:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I meditate from here to there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.42,0:16:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'm who I always was until four.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.42,0:16:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I meditate from five to six.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.42,0:16:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It tends to get compartmentalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.42,0:16:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.42,0:16:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you don't change what you're doing, you're going to keep getting what you're getting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So to apply that which you see to the way you are in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.48,0:16:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So the contemplation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.48,0:16:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it's the all-day fulfillment of what you've achieved within meditation, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.48,0:16:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.61,0:16:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And in your third book, you talk about meditating in context rather than the content of a mantra or following the breath and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.67,0:16:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Where, without going into that, I don't mean to Bogart that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.67,0:17:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No, each of these spiritual practices is befitting a certain level of the progression of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.67,0:17:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So there are things that are useful at this level.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They're hanging to the past at this level.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's things that will take you from this level to the next level.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's a time to walk the maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a time to do the rosary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.67,0:17:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a time to do sackcloth and ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.67,0:17:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a time to do asceticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.67,0:17:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a time to do selfless service.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.67,0:17:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's not a linear logical progression.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.74,0:17:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So something may be of need and appeal to you at a certain level.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.74,0:17:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.74,0:17:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And at other times, it could be an evasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.83,0:17:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is a spiritual, beneficial practice here could be an evasion here, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.83,0:17:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.83,0:17:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.83,0:17:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be a dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.16,0:17:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I just want to thank you for coming back into our world and writing those three incredible books.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.18,0:18:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And it seems like it must have taken an awful lot of effort because, you know, we're all in this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.28,0:18:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.28,0:18:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.28,0:18:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just, when I see you speaking and you seem to recall some of that time in your life before you came back, it seems like you really start to bliss out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And you could just go out there and just stay there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And I really appreciate you coming back and helping the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't really talk about those states when they begin to take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.00,0:18:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, you've got to draw back into, again, to the personage, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And I remind myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, the communicative transmitter of communication.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.51,0:18:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides, there's plenty of time on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.50,0:18:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that's a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:18:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got forever when you get there, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, my question is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to do what you've got to do while you're down there, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.63,0:19:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.63,0:19:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, I'm doing the lessons in the course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.63,0:19:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And I haven't read the text.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.63,0:19:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't read the text deliberately because of what you said about how it demonizes the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you watch for the demonization of the ego, you'll see it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.63,0:19:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a mistake to set up a duality within yourself already, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So is it worthwhile to read the text?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.86,0:19:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Or are you better off reading Huang Po or Maharachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.86,0:19:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it worth reading the text, I guess, is my point?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd have to reread it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been many a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.86,0:19:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.86,0:19:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't fall in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.86,0:19:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be aware of the demonization.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.86,0:19:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Just watch that downside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.86,0:19:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That downside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.86,0:19:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,See, once you've heard the truth, anything that's in error in what you read will stand
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.86,0:19:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,out of its own, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.95,0:19:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll say, well, that's demonizing the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.95,0:19:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you know, it shrieks and claws at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.95,0:20:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is, it's also true from a certain other level of abstraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego is the dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.95,0:20:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the Komodo dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.95,0:20:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.95,0:20:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And it will, frankly, throw you over the cliff to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.95,0:20:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than surrender, it'll throw you over the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.95,0:20:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll kill you over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.95,0:20:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll stay away from the text.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to demonize the text.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just saying there is a fault in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do the workbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see, the textbook does calibrate 50 points lower than the workbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.95,0:20:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So it is reflected there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.95,0:20:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And it sort of stands out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.95,0:20:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you've heard the truth, you say, well, the interpreter, the translator maybe just
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,translated it incorrectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.02,0:20:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A man shrieks and claws at you in quotes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's not really doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But you perceive it as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So a clarification of that I think would help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:21:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I had to rewrite that paragraph, I'd say you perceive it as shrieking and clawing
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.02,0:21:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,at you, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.02,0:21:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.02,0:21:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your projection.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.02,0:21:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how you're seeing the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.02,0:21:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.02,0:21:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I also heard something about a group OM.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.02,0:21:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if we could maybe do that before we leave today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.02,0:21:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Edward, you said you were going to hear OM?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.11,0:21:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say anything about having an OM.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.11,0:21:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.21,0:21:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.21,0:21:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.21,0:21:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say anything about an OM.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.21,0:21:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to say MO, and I got it backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.24,0:21:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't say MO.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.24,0:21:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We met.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.24,0:21:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We met.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.24,0:21:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.24,0:21:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I said we'd go home at 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.24,0:21:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.24,0:21:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Phyllis Hartzler.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.24,0:21:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from Pennsylvania.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.33,0:21:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just wanted to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really have a question that I can think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.66,0:21:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll be quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.66,0:21:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.66,0:21:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.66,0:21:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.66,0:21:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.66,0:21:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.66,0:21:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what's the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.66,0:21:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we have time on the line?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.66,0:21:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.66,0:21:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's Locke, and I just live down the road in Cornville.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.66,0:22:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.66,0:22:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.66,0:22:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.66,0:22:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.42,0:22:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.96,0:22:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.96,0:22:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.66,0:22:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.66,0:22:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.66,0:22:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.66,0:22:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.66,0:22:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.66,0:22:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.66,0:22:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.66,0:22:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.64,0:22:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You live in Cornville?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.64,0:22:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.64,0:22:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, lucky man.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.64,0:22:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Good karma, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.64,0:22:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.64,0:22:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I live at .
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.64,0:22:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.09,0:22:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You said something during the lecture about a bomb killing so many people and, so, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.64,0:22:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Not having a judgment about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.34,0:22:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And I remember in a previous lifetime I was a young pastor for a particular church, and
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.31,0:22:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I was talking to this older pastor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.67,0:22:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and a bird flew and hit the window and fell down into the bushes and he just
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.32,0:23:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,calmly he calmly got up and got the bird and held on to it until it woke up and
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.78,0:23:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,took off and I remember thinking I don't know I don't know shit about compassion
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.04,0:23:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and and and and I guess my question is
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.27,0:23:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,you know how you know I mean I mean my my I was like so what so you know I've
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.35,0:23:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,seen birds hit the window all the time so but I think that so what that I was
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.83,0:23:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,having at that time is different than the so what that you're talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.73,0:23:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm wondering if you could just sort of you know how can I be compassionate
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.35,0:23:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,without making a judgment about something how can you avoid making a
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.75,0:23:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.05,0:23:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.95,0:23:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,well you just become compassionate towards all of life in all of its
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.99,0:24:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,expressions whether it's a busload of children being blown up or a bird
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.23,0:24:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,hitting the window you see that that is the interaction that's the way creation
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.79,0:24:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,unfolds and that's the karma of each entity you know physicality and the
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.45,0:24:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,temporality that goes with physicality that's one reason enlightenment is to go
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.49,0:24:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond that physicality and so that you're not run over on the road anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.29,0:24:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,see that bird had really good karma
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.91,0:24:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that picked him up sure yeah really good karma and and and and the I mean I mean
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.37,0:24:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I did the minister and you go oh my god I can't believe this cruel world and
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.63,0:24:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,birds hit the window oh yeah like that it was sort of like he just he just knew
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.23,0:24:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,what needed to be done he wasn't oh yeah judgmental place well no that's because
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.01,0:24:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the way you are that's the way you are you cherish all of life in all of its
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.93,0:24:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,expressions and that's the way you are you cherish all of life in all of its expressions
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.29,0:24:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you see it could be flowers it can be the bird you know compassion for all of
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.08,0:25:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,life in all its expressions it's just a way of being with the world you know
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.64,0:25:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you already appreciate that so that means you're already that way yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.70,0:25:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,otherwise you wouldn't have been impressed by what he did yes my name is
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.77,0:25:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Jackie I'm from California I read your books in the end of last year and came
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.83,0:25:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,to my first seminar in December went home and all
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.43,0:25:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,heaven or hell broke loose big time yes I remember you saying that from the
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.35,0:25:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,December seminar two things I took home with me whatever isn't integrous in your
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.15,0:25:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,life in all areas in whatever area yeah would fall by the wayside the world
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.89,0:25:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,comes will show up yeah and and whatever happens just say so what I've been saying
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.27,0:25:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,so many times I've been saying so many times I've been saying so many times I've been saying so many times I've been saying so many times
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.43,0:26:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,so what every day you know I I'm an RN I had my own practice I closed that due
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.07,0:26:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,to other situations my husband had had an alcoholic problem for a long time and
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.87,0:26:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I had told him he needs to do something about this or I was going to walk away
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.61,0:26:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,because I I felt it was infringing on even my health and my stress from it so
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.51,0:26:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,he said fine I'm going to do something about this because I felt it was
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.59,0:26:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,infringing on even my stress from it so I felt it was infringing on even my stress from it so I thought hey he went to a hey
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.59,0:26:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to a hey he went to he stayed sober for a week came home and told me
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.73,0:27:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,her lectures can be helped by the
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.76,0:27:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,current marriage girl
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.46,0:27:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,this Oh I love
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.98,0:27:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, the prayer of permission to be released from the relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.02,0:27:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,if the alcoholism couldn't be brought under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.20,0:27:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.72,0:27:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I had prayed a prayer similar to what you had said to pray,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.30,0:27:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,which was the third thing I took home,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.92,0:27:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,is whatever time I have left, I dedicate it all to your service.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.52,0:27:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.24,0:27:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever's left.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.12,0:28:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If I die tonight, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.28,0:28:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,C'est la vie.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.80,0:28:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's when everything hit the fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.26,0:28:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.49,0:28:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.25,0:28:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You can talk then.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.95,0:28:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you talk then?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.41,0:28:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm at a loss to even know what's going to be next.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.72,0:28:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.92,0:28:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.78,0:28:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.39,0:28:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You still don't know what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.55,0:28:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You still don't know what it means to not.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.15,0:28:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You still don't know what it means to not resist it and to not seek it,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.49,0:28:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to be neutral.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.65,0:28:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.33,0:28:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is that neutral?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.69,0:28:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If it happens, it happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.77,0:28:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If it doesn't happen, it doesn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.19,0:28:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's okay that it's happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.39,0:28:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.75,0:28:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't throw you about in the boat, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.53,0:28:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.05,0:28:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've maintained a certain equilibrium
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.61,0:28:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,at things that would throw in a lot of people themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.05,0:28:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.87,0:29:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you're somehow liberated,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.77,0:29:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,so you've got some kind of a freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.01,0:29:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm free as a bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.95,0:29:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're free as a bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.63,0:29:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.15,0:29:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're free as a bird,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.57,0:29:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and now you just maintain your spiritual balance,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.23,0:29:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and what is ready for you will come upon you as the next hello,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.43,0:29:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.41,0:29:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.14,0:29:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And you just keep going along with it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.44,0:29:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.72,0:29:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.88,0:29:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.26,0:29:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.08,0:29:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a plan somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.14,0:29:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to somehow believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.64,0:29:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a plan somewhere in the confusion,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.16,0:29:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,because it wouldn't have blown up like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.38,0:29:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.52,0:29:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be a set trigger,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.18,0:29:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're taking a jump in consciousness that released it,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.00,0:29:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,so that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.84,0:29:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.84,0:30:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We look forward to the next installment.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.41,0:30:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she should only come to every other lecture, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.40,0:30:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're speaking to both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.10,0:30:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.04,0:30:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to stand in front of this here?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.20,0:30:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.72,0:30:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, that won't go too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.95,0:30:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.21,0:30:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll stand here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.67,0:30:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't recognize that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.97,0:30:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that something I wrote?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.09,0:30:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.63,0:30:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.57,0:30:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.44,0:30:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.98,0:30:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.54,0:30:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a question he wants to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.54,0:30:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.84,0:30:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.24,0:30:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My question, you mentioned today
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.00,0:30:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that we have a responsibility to respect our assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.90,0:30:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A responsibility, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.90,0:30:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,To respect the assets that we are given,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.12,0:30:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,to be stewards to our assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.68,0:30:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.38,0:30:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.70,0:30:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How does one reconcile, for example,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.58,0:30:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,if your asset,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.84,0:30:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,is in the business world,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.28,0:31:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and your intention is enlightenment,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.24,0:31:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,however it comes,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.42,0:31:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,how do you reconcile
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.34,0:31:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,having a sense of responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.40,0:31:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to participate in daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.40,0:31:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,activating your assets in the business world,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.72,0:31:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet at the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.26,0:31:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,reach a state of enlightenment,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.56,0:31:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,which could render you completely unable
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.88,0:31:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to fulfill those assets?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.88,0:31:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.18,0:31:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.94,0:31:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.90,0:31:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a matter of attachment
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.16,0:31:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and the way in which you contextualize its value.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.69,0:31:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you've got to do something with your body
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.53,0:31:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,while you hang out waiting to be enlightened,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.27,0:31:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.41,0:31:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And you might as well be using it for the good of mankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.39,0:31:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,whether it's producing a product.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.55,0:31:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you know, I need a pen to sign things with.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.03,0:31:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody's got to make the pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.71,0:31:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody's got to ship it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.79,0:31:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be boxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.39,0:31:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you know, the qualities of human life are multiple.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.67,0:31:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So we serve each other in multiple ways,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.03,0:32:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,multiple ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.37,0:32:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So I say if you're in business,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.42,0:32:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,then see what that value is to the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.72,0:32:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the employee to the employees
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.32,0:32:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,as the source of employment, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.15,0:32:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So it serves multiple functions.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.97,0:32:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you see its intrinsic value,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.11,0:32:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.91,0:32:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,you're neither attracted
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.39,0:32:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,nor do you have an aversion to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.81,0:32:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just what,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.69,0:32:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,then after a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.19,0:32:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you stop identifying,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.25,0:32:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you're identifying with the body
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.09,0:32:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and you see that's a phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.87,0:32:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a phenomena of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.87,0:32:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't need a personal you to make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.13,0:32:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You may have initiated it,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.13,0:32:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but now it's going to have like a life
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.65,0:32:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,or an energy of its own
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.89,0:32:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,to which you have a certain responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.57,0:32:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the degree of involvement is something different.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.07,0:32:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So responsibility is one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.89,0:32:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Involvement is another.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.65,0:32:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can find somebody to run the factory
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.59,0:32:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,while you join an ashram,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.63,0:32:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,so why?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.25,0:32:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.38,0:32:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.72,0:32:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.02,0:32:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't find somebody to run the factory
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.40,0:33:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're all going to lose their jobs
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.24,0:33:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and the factory's going to close
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.06,0:33:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and the townspeople are going to go poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.98,0:33:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's going to hold you in there
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.22,0:33:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,until you find somebody, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.59,0:33:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that can hold it together
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.63,0:33:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,for the sake of the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.48,0:33:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So once you've activated that energy
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.66,0:33:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you are, in effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.86,0:33:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,neutral to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.26,0:33:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you can then go on your own personal path
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.68,0:33:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,knowing that that asset of yours
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.68,0:33:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is alive and has its own momentum.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.30,0:33:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so you try to find
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.88,0:33:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,somebody that will fulfill that function for you
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.54,0:33:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and thereby free yourself, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.60,0:33:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I was chief of staff
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.36,0:33:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,at Girls Ranch there in Prescott
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.84,0:33:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,for many years
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.20,0:33:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,because there wasn't any doctor around.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.50,0:33:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, how am I going to get out of there?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.84,0:33:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no other doctor around,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.46,0:33:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.40,0:33:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're like hooked
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.34,0:33:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,until you find somebody that could take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.28,0:33:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And the same with the nursing homes, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.34,0:33:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,until finally the county could find somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.50,0:33:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So you sort of stayed out of a sense of responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.80,0:33:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and obligation.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.66,0:34:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, eventually, you get released from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.32,0:34:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You get too old to do it, for God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.92,0:34:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Age releases you at the end, thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.62,0:34:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be ready to quit,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.00,0:34:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but the old reaper is going to take you out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.68,0:34:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.63,0:34:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a good friend of the reaper,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.61,0:34:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,just when you need him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.36,0:34:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.06,0:34:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooked you out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.90,0:34:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.62,0:34:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.30,0:34:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Beverly from Dallas.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.50,0:34:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We found your books this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.35,0:34:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And we watched your videos all for last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.81,0:34:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm just so appreciative for what you've done
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.23,0:34:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and for God giving me, you know, this chance again.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.67,0:34:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And so my question, I really formed at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.61,0:34:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought, well, I want to get a question
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.37,0:34:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,so I can talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.65,0:34:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.17,0:34:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.91,0:35:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So my question, and I don't really care
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.04,0:35:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,whether it's right or wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.88,0:35:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but can you reach enlightenment reading your books?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.52,0:35:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, interesting question.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.66,0:35:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I would presume that putting it into practice
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.39,0:35:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,is what makes the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.31,0:35:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,However, even to have heard of it already changes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.36,0:35:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, even the Buddha said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.27,0:35:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Rare is it to be a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.71,0:35:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Extremely rare in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.09,0:35:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarer still.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.89,0:35:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarer still is it to have heard of enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.07,0:35:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And rarest of all is having heard of it to pursue it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.47,0:35:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.94,0:35:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, it's a great gift to be a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.22,0:35:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a great gift to even hear of enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.90,0:35:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's certainly a great gift to be attracted to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.20,0:35:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.00,0:35:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortunate, karmically fortunate are we
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.44,0:35:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that we've even heard of it and esteemed it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.46,0:35:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,or respected, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.02,0:35:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.92,0:36:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When you start carrying around,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.10,0:36:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, Huang Po under your arm,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.96,0:36:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, you're getting there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.26,0:36:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.28,0:36:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't read that yet, but we've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.49,0:36:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huang Po or the aphorisms of, et cetera, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.83,0:36:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They became enlightened in a different culture
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.57,0:36:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and they expressed it in a different way.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.55,0:36:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And, but they become respected, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.04,0:36:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,ancestors respected, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.79,0:36:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I didn't want to cry because my husband is here
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.91,0:36:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and we want to get a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.57,0:36:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.05,0:36:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's got a dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.49,0:36:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.15,0:36:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't either.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.33,0:36:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm resigning the dollar fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.67,0:36:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no one else, you have to tell the story
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.57,0:36:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,because nobody else is going to buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.35,0:36:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.93,0:36:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.83,0:36:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We put it in the dollar bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.93,0:36:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.90,0:36:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.58,0:36:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell everyone the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.00,0:36:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.40,0:36:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.80,0:36:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you the whole story now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.44,0:36:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.66,0:36:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was in the Himalayas.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.50,0:36:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it was in the Alps.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.80,0:36:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.80,0:36:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It was in the Himalayas.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.90,0:36:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.14,0:37:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No other freaking place.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.42,0:37:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Machu Picchu.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.14,0:37:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.84,0:37:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Peru.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.96,0:37:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The Andes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.78,0:37:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The high up in the Andes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.18,0:37:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The Andes in Peru are just mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.52,0:37:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, just wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.55,0:37:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And Machu Picchu, of course, is impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.97,0:37:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.99,0:37:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.43,0:37:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's Mike and I'm from Dallas.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.29,0:37:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And that beautiful spirit has been in my life for 40 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.58,0:37:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So we share a lot in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.88,0:37:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wanted to also thank you and express our gratitude
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.62,0:37:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,for what you...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.94,0:37:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.40,0:37:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.46,0:37:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.48,0:37:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You've meant to us as you've been in our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.52,0:37:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The question I have is some clarification
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.96,0:37:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,in regards to causality versus intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.26,0:37:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Or causality and intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.72,0:37:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard you say that when you snip the apple,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.81,0:37:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you didn't cause it to drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.31,0:37:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.57,0:37:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The field did.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.17,0:37:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The gravity did.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.77,0:37:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Gravity did, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.67,0:38:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you've also said that when you have...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.23,0:38:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,With the Empire State Bill,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.69,0:38:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,that there was a an intention that went in there and into the field of an
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.69,0:38:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,infinite potentiality yeah right so my question is could the snipping of the
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.35,0:38:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple be the intention in the infinite field of potentiality that yeah brings
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.58,0:38:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the actualization of the intention well it was you see potentiality becomes
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.08,0:38:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,actuality when conditions are favorable oh so it's favorable because all you do
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.13,0:38:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not going to cause the Apple to fall you're going to just change the
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.75,0:38:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,timing of it because come foot you know in autumn it's going to drop of its own
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.55,0:38:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,so you're just trying to jump it up so
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.63,0:39:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,intentionality then becomes potentiality when the conditions
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.75,0:39:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,to
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.73,0:39:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,facilitate that actuality are present so it doesn't like otherwise you would have
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.85,0:39:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,life going against itself you know I'm saying linear life at least going
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.05,0:39:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,against itself so the potentiality then is extremely powerful powerful you might
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.52,0:39:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,say all of creation is the actualization of the potentiality of the will of God
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.31,0:39:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,who only had to say yes to the spark and foreverness evolved
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.16,0:39:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,within the third three dimensional world okay a follow-up question is it
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.20,0:39:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,seemed like when you've talked about the lower levels of consciousness that that
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.48,0:39:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a big attractor field and they get more of what were they're resonating
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.80,0:40:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,for their realizing isn't theontology I guess with the intention is it in Jagl
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.98,0:40:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Arif this kind of thing or is there a but Minute
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.52,0:40:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,level consciousness and then the togetherness of the consciousness I can
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.66,0:40:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,potentiality is
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.35,0:40:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,potentiated at that point
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.83,0:40:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,at a higher level of consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.39,0:40:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, because you contextualize the whole thing
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.79,0:40:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,different, your intention is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.75,0:40:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So I say the reason
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.99,0:40:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,you should prepare for enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.91,0:40:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is because
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.71,0:40:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody here is already committed to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.49,0:40:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,aligned with it, they're studying
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.15,0:40:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,it, practicing it, well, the end is
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.05,0:40:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,uncertain, unless you do something
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.13,0:40:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,to make it, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.69,0:40:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to refuse it. It's going to constantly
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.03,0:40:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,unfold to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.39,0:40:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And whatever the way that you
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.11,0:40:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,need to see to go, it's going to be like
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.09,0:40:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly illuminated, you suddenly see this
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.15,0:40:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,pathway over here, and if you hadn't
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.05,0:40:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,chosen enlightenment, you wouldn't see that pathway
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.09,0:40:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,over there. So
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.66,0:40:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,those things are not definable,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.92,0:40:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but you've obviously
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.16,0:40:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,changed the course
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.30,0:41:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,of events, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.22,0:41:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, very good, thanks again.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.26,0:41:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Dallas, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.62,0:41:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.37,0:41:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.33,0:41:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The chair is like right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.45,0:41:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but the box is pointing
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.71,0:41:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,different. Well, I moved in because
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.40,0:41:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody was sitting in the room. It's hard for them to get
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.72,0:41:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,in and out, but the chair is out that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.05,0:41:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.06,0:41:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, I have
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.52,0:41:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,enjoyed your chanting Aum
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.00,0:41:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,when you have done so in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.28,0:41:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,With your permission, may we have quiet
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.24,0:41:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,from the audience, and would you give us
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.40,0:41:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,as comfortable as you can
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.26,0:41:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,a nice, long, and deep
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.20,0:41:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Aum, also for the purpose
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.26,0:41:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,for those who purchase a tape,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.46,0:41:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,so that we can listen to your Aum
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.46,0:41:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,at the end of the seminar later.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.46,0:41:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We can listen to your Aum
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.46,0:42:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to our hearts content.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.96,0:42:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You told us that you aren't allowed to do the octopus
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.96,0:42:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,anymore, so
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.96,0:42:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,my friends and I would like to give you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.96,0:42:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, isn't that adorable?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.65,0:42:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. My friends have the questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.65,0:42:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.65,0:42:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.65,0:42:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an adorable octopus.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.65,0:42:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always admired them.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.25,0:42:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible entity.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.18,0:42:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, look at the eyes here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.18,0:42:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.18,0:42:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Um,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.84,0:43:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,my question is in regards to assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.84,0:43:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it important
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.16,0:43:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,to know your assets?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.16,0:43:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm wondering,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.16,0:43:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,is mediocrity an asset?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.16,0:43:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a great
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.33,0:43:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,liberation.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.90,0:43:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,To be a virtuoso, an expert,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.90,0:43:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.60,0:43:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is quite a pressure, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.44,0:43:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,To be a world champion chess player once,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.44,0:43:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,your life is screwed, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.44,0:43:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially if you're beat by
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.44,0:43:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Blue. Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.14,0:43:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life is hell, thenceforth.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.14,0:43:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, no, mediocrity
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.26,0:43:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is a way of being sort of at
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.26,0:43:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,neutral. And I think
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.39,0:43:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,sometimes the spirit, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.39,0:43:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,takes sort of a rest
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.39,0:43:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and goes on vacation for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.39,0:44:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I think this one,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.48,0:44:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, when I just have a
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.48,0:44:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,easy life, have a good family,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.48,0:44:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,a good job, and
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.48,0:44:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,let it be at that and learn to enjoy
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.48,0:44:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.48,0:44:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, to enjoy that which
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.48,0:44:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you are may be the lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.48,0:44:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,To appreciate and see the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.48,0:44:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,value of enjoying of being nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.48,0:44:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.03,0:44:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,being nobody is wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.85,0:44:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to being somebody,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.85,0:44:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,it has a great payoff, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.85,0:44:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're driving down the road
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.85,0:44:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,in the truck and nobody knows you from Adam,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.85,0:44:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're not
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.27,0:44:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,beholden to anybody,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.27,0:44:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,don't have to be anywhere, don't have to sign anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.27,0:44:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,don't have to vote on anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.27,0:44:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,don't have to be quoted, don't have to appear
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.27,0:44:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,on television or radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.16,0:44:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a free bird. Are you letting anybody
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.16,0:44:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,down by doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.16,0:44:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course, the word needs you to save them,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.16,0:44:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but it'll do without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.16,0:44:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I mean, if you, like you talked about
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.16,0:45:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,being responsible for your
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.16,0:45:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,assets, right? Well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.16,0:45:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your asset? So, your asset is
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.16,0:45:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the learning of the value
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.16,0:45:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,of just being ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.16,0:45:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's learning
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.16,0:45:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,to live without specialness.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.16,0:45:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,See, the ego wants specialness.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.26,0:45:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And it wants specialness of relationships
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.26,0:45:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and goods and values
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.26,0:45:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and titles and recognitions and
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.26,0:45:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,it wants to voice its opinion about
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.26,0:45:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.52,0:45:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So, to learn to live
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.77,0:45:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,in that space is extremely valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.77,0:45:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you can be with God
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.43,0:45:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,there. You just be with it
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.43,0:45:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,there. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.65,0:45:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Any progressive demands will appear
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.86,0:45:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,only too soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.36,0:45:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The next emotional
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.87,0:45:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,tsunami. Thank you both
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.41,0:45:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,for being here today. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.41,0:45:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.41,0:45:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,When you talked about working with the girls
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.41,0:45:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,at the ranch,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.86,0:46:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,when we work with people that are
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.86,0:46:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,at these levels, I see today
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.86,0:46:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that you have amusements. You can say,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.86,0:46:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you can laugh at people in
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.86,0:46:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the below 200 non-integrist
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.86,0:46:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.86,0:46:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But some of us in the trenches, it's hard
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.86,0:46:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to maintain
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.89,0:46:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,a sense of
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.47,0:46:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,humor.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.47,0:46:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to continue in a
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.47,0:46:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,positive space when
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.47,0:46:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,you're working with a lot, especially
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.47,0:46:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,people in alcoholism.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.47,0:46:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, and some don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.47,0:46:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have tools
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.47,0:46:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,in that area? Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.94,0:46:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,professional detachment is something
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.94,0:46:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,you learn. And eventually
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.94,0:46:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,you learn compassion without attachment.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.94,0:46:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And attachment
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.94,0:46:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,is trying to exert your will on
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.94,0:46:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,outcomes. So
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.16,0:46:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you learn to serve
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.16,0:46:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever you can serve, because
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.16,0:46:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,it's your
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.16,0:46:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,turn to hold their hand, but you're
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.16,0:46:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,not the last one in line.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.16,0:47:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And they'll be going down to the next hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.16,0:47:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.16,0:47:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So you serve your function to the best of
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.16,0:47:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,your ability, and
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.16,0:47:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you convey the message. You can carry
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.16,0:47:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the message, you can't carry the person.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.16,0:47:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you convey the
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.35,0:47:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,options, and many people
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.08,0:47:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,will choose the negative,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.47,0:47:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,many people would rather die
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.47,0:47:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,than give in. You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.47,0:47:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I tell them, you get behind the car
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.97,0:47:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,one more time, they're gonna
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.97,0:47:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,put you away for
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.00,0:47:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,five years. What do you
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.58,0:47:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,think the first thing you did when you got home was?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.58,0:47:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You got in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.58,0:47:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you see, you can't
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.47,0:47:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,force them to be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.56,0:47:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The other
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.48,0:47:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,question I had for you is about
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.48,0:47:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,location. You moved here from New York,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.48,0:47:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and are there different
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.48,0:47:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,places that are easier for us to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.48,0:47:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And when we're in certain places,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.48,0:47:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,is
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.48,0:48:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the job harder?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.60,0:48:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to me sometimes it's harder. I'm in Phoenix
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.60,0:48:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.40,0:48:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is what harder? The environment?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.40,0:48:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the enlightenment harder?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.40,0:48:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The journey more difficult?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.40,0:48:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you convert it into
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.40,0:48:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever it's gonna be.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.40,0:48:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You convert anything
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.40,0:48:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,anywhere to
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.40,0:48:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,subserve your overall
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.40,0:48:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.68,0:48:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You pass through the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.68,0:48:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,doorways
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.68,0:48:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in multiple circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.68,0:48:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.54,0:48:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The rich and the famous, the poor and the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.54,0:48:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,infamous, it's all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.15,0:48:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? Hi. So, I'm in
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.36,0:48:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the process of surrender
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.36,0:48:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,for spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.55,0:48:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.55,0:49:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And I seem to be
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.55,0:49:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,losing
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.64,0:49:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,parts of my right side
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.64,0:49:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,in the process. Your right thigh?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.64,0:49:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Side.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.64,0:49:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Like my right eye, my right
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.64,0:49:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.00,0:49:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They seem to be busy somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.00,0:49:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I wonder
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.00,0:49:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,if you could
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.09,0:49:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,explain surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.09,0:49:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm confused on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.09,0:49:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is this just part of the
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.09,0:49:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,process? It has to do with the will.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.09,0:49:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.09,0:49:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All spiritual work
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.09,0:49:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,centers on the fulcrum of the will.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.09,0:49:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only by the ascent of the will.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.09,0:49:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's by the ascent of the will
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.09,0:49:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,that your karmic
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.09,0:49:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,destiny is
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.12,0:49:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,set, and the calibrated level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.12,0:49:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,is set, because the two go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.12,0:49:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only by the
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.64,0:49:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,will. So, the surrender
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.64,0:49:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,is surrender of what? It's
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.64,0:49:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,surrender of volition, of
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.64,0:49:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,will, and
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.96,0:49:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to control. So, the will
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.96,0:49:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,expresses itself in ordinary life.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.96,0:50:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's trying to control.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.08,0:50:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And willpower, you know, is very
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.08,0:50:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,weak. Everybody's tried
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.37,0:50:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,willpower, and so the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.37,0:50:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,will of the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.37,0:50:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,is relatively weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.37,0:50:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The will of the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.82,0:50:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates at exactly the same level
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.82,0:50:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,as your personal level.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.98,0:50:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if you're at 205 and you exert
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.98,0:50:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,your will, the power of that will
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.98,0:50:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to be at 205,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.97,0:50:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,which may tip the balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.97,0:50:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The invocation, see,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.12,0:50:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,will with a capital W is the will of
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.12,0:50:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,God. And when you surrender
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.12,0:50:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,to God's
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.16,0:50:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,will, that means you've removed
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.16,0:50:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,your own resistance and positionalities
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.16,0:50:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and vanities. Now
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.16,0:50:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,you've opened the door,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.35,0:50:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and the spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.35,0:50:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,will, the will of God
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.64,0:50:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,as you experience it within,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.64,0:50:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates at 850. Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.64,0:50:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, 850 will
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.64,0:50:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,knock just about anything
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.64,0:50:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,off the path.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.86,0:51:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the personal will
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.40,0:51:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,then is insufficient to overcome
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.40,0:51:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,even a
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.40,0:51:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,bad habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.07,0:51:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The divine will, however, is enormously
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.07,0:51:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,powerful. So, when you invite in
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.07,0:51:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,divine will, then be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.07,0:51:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.93,0:51:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Be prepared when you invite in divine
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.93,0:51:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,will, because it may
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.35,0:51:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,sweep people right out of your
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.67,0:51:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,family situation, may sweep you right
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.67,0:51:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,from one part of the country to another, may change
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.67,0:51:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,your health. You may go from wealth
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.63,0:51:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to poverty or vice versa.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.63,0:51:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is by volition.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.63,0:51:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? No, it's not
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.63,0:51:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,by volition, it's by the will of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.63,0:51:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Volition, then, is personal will.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.63,0:51:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You might say willfulness,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.63,0:51:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,even though you purify
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.63,0:51:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,it with a spiritual sounding goal,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.63,0:51:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,it's still willfulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.63,0:51:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's willful
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.39,0:51:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,to even insist that you're going to be enlightened,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.39,0:51:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,right? Who wants to be enlightened?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.68,0:52:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego wants to be enlightened, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.68,0:52:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if you surrender
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.74,0:52:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,then the will to God, and you say
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.74,0:52:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I align myself with
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.74,0:52:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,thee, O Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.00,0:52:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that I may be thy servant,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.00,0:52:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that I may fulfill my infinite potential
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.00,0:52:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to thy glory, you know, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.00,0:52:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this as a way of being
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.00,0:52:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world now
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.00,0:52:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,invites divine will.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.00,0:52:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, as I say, you're about
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.32,0:52:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,better be prepared, because whatever it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.32,0:52:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,throwing you off a cliff to get it,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.32,0:52:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,that's what happens, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.08,0:52:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why the 12-step
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.23,0:52:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,programs are so powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.77,0:52:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You admit that you're powerless,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.77,0:52:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,well, then invoke the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.41,0:52:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,will of God. So you're
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.41,0:52:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,getting rid of something that
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.41,0:52:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates below 200, or you wouldn't be
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.41,0:52:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,having a problem with addiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.41,0:52:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're inviting in the miraculous,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.41,0:52:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,as everybody will tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.41,0:52:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It was not of their own self
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.57,0:53:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,they recovered, it was
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.57,0:53:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.59,0:53:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So, early on in your lecture
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.59,0:53:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you calibrated that 90%,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.59,0:53:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,only 90% of the
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.59,0:53:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'd say roughly 90% of the people in the
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.59,0:53:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,audience will reach enlightenment, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.59,0:53:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all destined, but only 90%
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.59,0:53:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,will get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.59,0:53:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.59,0:53:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,10% will stop over at the casino
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.59,0:53:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,for a few...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.59,0:53:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But will they
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.59,0:53:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,reach enlightenment at some point?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.59,0:53:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you worried about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.59,0:53:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.59,0:53:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I let God worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.59,0:53:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.59,0:53:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just an estimation.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.45,0:53:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,As I say,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.52,0:53:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,we tend to sweep in together,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.52,0:53:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.52,0:53:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that 10%, maybe after a few
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.52,0:53:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,catastrophic disasters, will
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.52,0:53:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,shift, you know. But, you know, enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.52,0:53:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,is a great rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.52,0:53:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Only 1 in 10 million
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.93,0:54:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,even think of it as a plausible
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.93,0:54:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,alternative.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.83,0:54:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, 10 million people
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.83,0:54:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,on the street. What is your main
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.83,0:54:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,ambition in life?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.96,0:54:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,1 in 10 million will tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.96,0:54:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,to realize God
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.12,0:54:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,or to become enlightened, or
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.12,0:54:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,you know. 1 in 10 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.12,0:54:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And that doesn't mean they're good
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.69,0:54:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,at it, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.20,0:54:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So, rare it is to be born a human
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.20,0:54:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,to have heard of enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.68,0:54:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And rarest of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.03,0:54:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to be born a human, to have heard
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.03,0:54:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,it, and then to seek it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.03,0:54:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.44,0:54:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who call upon me
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.34,0:54:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,are dear to me, said Krishna.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.34,0:54:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The 91st Psalm
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.84,0:54:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,says the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.42,0:54:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,To those who place all
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.42,0:54:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,their faith in me,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.90,0:55:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the miraculous shall be
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.90,0:55:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,spread before them. See?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.64,0:55:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The same thing is said in all
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.64,0:55:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,great religions.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.92,0:55:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who call upon divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.92,0:55:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,surrender their life
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.92,0:55:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to the service of divinity,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.96,0:55:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you become dear to divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.96,0:55:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And divinity looks
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.96,0:55:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,after its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.72,0:55:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the 10% is unwilling to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.72,0:55:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They wish to keep it as a function
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.74,0:55:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,of the personal world. See?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.74,0:55:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Enlightened will be
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.74,0:55:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,when I want it. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.74,0:55:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Enlightened may be never.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.90,0:55:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.76,0:55:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? If I'm God and I say,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.76,0:55:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you surrender your enlightenment to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.76,0:55:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.08,0:55:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And it may not happen at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.08,0:55:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay? Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.08,0:55:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. If it's okay not to become enlightened,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.08,0:55:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,now you've earned the right to become enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.08,0:55:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.52,0:56:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,May have to repeat the same grade, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.52,0:56:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, a few times.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.52,0:56:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's actually
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.61,0:56:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,my concern or question, I guess,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.61,0:56:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is about worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.61,0:56:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I worry a lot, and it just keeps
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.61,0:56:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,repeating itself over
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.80,0:56:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.84,0:56:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've noticed, or I guess I've
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.84,0:56:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,become aware how much I worry
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.84,0:56:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and how much, I guess it's the attractor fields
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.84,0:56:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that I attract to myself, like kind of the chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.84,0:56:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid, or I worry about
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.84,0:56:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of things, so I think I create
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.84,0:56:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,all this chaos. Okay, so it's basically
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.84,0:56:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the unwillingness to surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.84,0:56:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, the illusion
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.96,0:56:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that constantly
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.96,0:56:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,working it over in your mind will
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.96,0:56:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,somehow solve it or change it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.96,0:56:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Whereas the opposite,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.96,0:56:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,if you surrender it to God and say, I can't do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.96,0:56:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,call the plumber.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.56,0:56:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you surrender it to the plumber.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.56,0:57:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't hang over on the plumber and tell him which way to pick it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.56,0:57:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.02,0:57:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,worrying is a way of thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.02,0:57:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that if you just keep persisting
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.02,0:57:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,on it long enough, you will change the result
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.02,0:57:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and gain control of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.31,0:57:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't. You just constantly entertain yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.31,0:57:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,with that thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.24,0:57:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a way of getting hooked into trying to control,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.24,0:57:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to control
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.24,0:57:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the outcome by sort of
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.24,0:57:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,worrying it and chewing it, chewing it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.24,0:57:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a natural human
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.36,0:57:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,characteristic.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.36,0:57:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a control issue?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.56,0:57:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I would think so. Could you let,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.56,0:57:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,to, the way really out of it is
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.56,0:57:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,to picture the worst possible
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.56,0:57:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,scenario. I do that a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.56,0:57:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.56,0:57:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to do that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.56,0:57:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And surrender yourself to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.56,0:57:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And then ask for God, God for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.56,0:57:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's, and some of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.56,0:57:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the reason they don't resolve
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.56,0:57:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,is that there's karmic
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.56,0:57:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,blockages of why it's
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.56,0:58:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,hanging out with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.56,0:58:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A certain problem
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.56,0:58:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,will persist and persist and persist.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.56,0:58:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.56,0:58:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And then finally, it relents.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.56,0:58:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you pull the little props
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.56,0:58:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,out from underneath it and then finally
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.56,0:58:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole avalanche collapses.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.56,0:58:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But, because you
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.56,0:58:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,experience it in time,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.56,0:58:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems trying, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.56,0:58:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any way
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.68,0:58:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I can speed it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.68,0:58:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.68,0:58:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,quit wanting to speed it up, it'll disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.68,0:58:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop resisting suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.62,0:58:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Choose to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.36,0:58:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I love to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.03,0:58:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I love the suffering of worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.03,0:58:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I love the anxiety of worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.03,0:58:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.03,0:58:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the way to get rid of a thing is by choosing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.03,0:58:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The way to experience a thing
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.03,0:58:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,is by resisting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.03,0:58:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So you only experience that which you resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.03,0:58:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So choose to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.03,0:58:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Your problem is you don't worry hard enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.64,0:59:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up earlier, I want you to sit there
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.64,0:59:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and I want you to really, really
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.64,0:59:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,worry. You're doing a
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.08,0:59:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,half-assed Jamba Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.08,0:59:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you able to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.53,0:59:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I eat. You can eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.53,0:59:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then you're not worrying hard enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.53,0:59:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're really worried,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.53,0:59:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,you're sick and you lose your appetite, so
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.53,0:59:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not worrying hard enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.42,0:59:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Worry harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.90,0:59:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to promise me
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.90,0:59:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're going to worry
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.90,0:59:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.90,0:59:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Harder. Are you going to
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.90,0:59:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,promise me or not? I want you to
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.99,0:59:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,promise me that you're
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.99,0:59:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,going to worry harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.99,0:59:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you do that or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.47,0:59:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I say about the will?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.98,0:59:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.33,1:00:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking you, would you please
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.46,1:00:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,worry harder? I'm the doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.46,1:00:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the patient.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.27,1:00:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Alright, you can even worry
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.27,1:00:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,by the clock. I want you to keep
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.81,1:00:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,a diary of your worry time.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.81,1:00:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.81,1:00:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,worry you can also calibrate on a one to ten
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.81,1:00:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,like pain. What's your worry
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.00,1:00:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,at now? Five?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.09,1:00:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Four? Six?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.09,1:00:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Four or five. Five out of five.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.09,1:00:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. You've got to focus on
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.50,1:00:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,worrying and worry up to about
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.50,1:00:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,a ten. I want you to really agonize
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.50,1:00:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and worry over the damn thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.66,1:00:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,When you lose your
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.66,1:00:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,appetite, you know you're at a ten.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.66,1:00:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.43,1:00:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,to keep it up as long as you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.43,1:00:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.61,1:00:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious? I am very serious.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.61,1:00:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm being videotaped.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.61,1:00:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm being
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.61,1:00:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,videotaped right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.61,1:01:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.68,1:01:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to promise
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.68,1:01:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,me you are going to worry hard.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.68,1:01:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Earnestly.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.87,1:01:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're holding back.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.87,1:01:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a joke?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.87,1:01:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your question. It's your answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.99,1:01:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not going to stop worrying about you,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.99,1:01:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,by God, I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.99,1:01:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really worried about
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.32,1:01:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,this lady.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.32,1:01:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She won't worry harder.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.32,1:01:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm really worried that if you don't worry
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.32,1:01:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,harder, you're going to be stuck with worrying this.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.32,1:01:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Work harder on worrying.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.44,1:01:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to blow off the carbon on the highway.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.44,1:01:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Run a ride up to 90, 95 and don't take
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.44,1:01:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,your foot off the exhaust.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.44,1:01:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.44,1:01:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the way you burn the carbon out of the valves, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.44,1:01:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.44,1:01:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Get on the road and run it. Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.44,1:01:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.44,1:01:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've got to go to the diary. Time diary.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.44,1:01:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Just keep worrying.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.44,1:01:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And give me
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.44,1:02:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,a one to ten.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.16,1:02:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You disappear that which you choose
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.16,1:02:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and you perpetuate that which you resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.72,1:02:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.72,1:02:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to thank you for having
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.72,1:02:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,accrued the karmas that led you
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.72,1:02:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,to stick around.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.78,1:02:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing the Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.78,1:02:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm at a point where
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.78,1:02:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asked to
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.78,1:02:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,listen for the voice for God.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.78,1:02:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.78,1:02:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm having trouble
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.32,1:02:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,both believing that
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.32,1:02:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,God has a voice
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.32,1:02:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and that I want to hear voices.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.22,1:02:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.80,1:02:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Cossack, we've got Thorothene.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.80,1:03:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.08,1:03:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,so it hasn't been revealed to you
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.08,1:03:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,what the voice of God sounds like.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.08,1:03:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.11,1:03:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear it?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.11,1:03:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.15,1:03:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.15,1:03:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now do you hear the voice of God?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.24,1:03:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It's present.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.14,1:03:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And all that exists,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.17,1:03:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,as it expresses it to you,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.17,1:03:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,everything is divinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.77,1:03:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how you see the beauty
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.77,1:03:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,that exists in everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.77,1:03:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Divinity reveals itself
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.77,1:03:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,as exquisite beauty of all that exists.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.77,1:03:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The presence of God is innate
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.60,1:03:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,within sound as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.60,1:03:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All sound is
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.52,1:04:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the voice of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.25,1:04:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You intuit the presence of God
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.25,1:04:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,in all that exists, all that speaks,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.25,1:04:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,all that stands,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.51,1:04:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,all that falls, all that breathes,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.51,1:04:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,all that thinks.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.76,1:04:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no other voice.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.98,1:04:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That one I want to hear.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.98,1:04:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.19,1:04:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, would you comment
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.19,1:04:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,on the relationship between
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.19,1:04:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the calibration of art
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.19,1:04:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and the calibration of the artist
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.19,1:04:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that created it?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.19,1:04:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, I think that you have said
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.19,1:04:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that Rembrandt's paintings calibrate
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.19,1:04:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,very high, perhaps 700.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.19,1:04:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Does Rembrandt calibrate 700?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.19,1:04:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I just calibrate the art.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.31,1:04:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Generally, the literary
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.31,1:05:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,product, the writing or the art
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.31,1:05:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,of a person will reflect exactly
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.31,1:05:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,their level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.31,1:05:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Generally, it's the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.31,1:05:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you would have to artificially
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.31,1:05:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,become that which you are not
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.31,1:05:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,to create something different
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.31,1:05:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,to what you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.56,1:05:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to be sort of a deliberate fake
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.56,1:05:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.84,1:05:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretend you're stupid when you're not.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.13,1:05:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.02,1:05:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of things become
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.10,1:05:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,obvious by paradox
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.10,1:05:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and humor.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.10,1:05:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I think paradox and humor.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.58,1:05:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's into piety
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.58,1:05:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and singing hymns
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.58,1:05:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and all, but I think
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.58,1:05:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,through humor, paradox,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.58,1:05:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,things become instantly
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.58,1:05:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,aware.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.35,1:06:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.94,1:06:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, when self-hatred
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.94,1:06:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,arises, how does one
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.20,1:06:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,work with that and accept it?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.20,1:06:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you handle it?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.39,1:06:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what do you get out of it,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.16,1:06:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,for one thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.46,1:06:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You get the fun of hating.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.35,1:06:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If hating wasn't enjoyable and fun,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.35,1:06:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,people wouldn't indulge in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.35,1:06:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a payoff to hating.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.73,1:06:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, you get to feel virtuous
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.73,1:06:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're hating evil and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.24,1:06:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what you're hating
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.24,1:06:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,is perceptions of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.24,1:06:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't even know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.24,1:06:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So any kind of a hatred is
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.24,1:06:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,some kind of a perception, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.24,1:06:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, maybe a mistake
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.43,1:06:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,or, you know, something.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.43,1:07:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're misperceiving it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.80,1:07:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you hate is a perception
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.80,1:07:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,because you don't know what the reality is.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.80,1:07:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you say,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.28,1:07:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate myself because I'm selfish.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.28,1:07:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the problem is you're not selfish enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.51,1:07:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I practice
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.65,1:07:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,being selfish?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.65,1:07:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If being selfish is what you hate
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.65,1:07:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,about yourself, then be
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.65,1:07:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,more selfish.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.55,1:07:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be the epitome of greed
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.55,1:07:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and gimme-ness.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.16,1:07:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I want more octopuses.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.60,1:07:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, because you're defeated
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.96,1:07:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,by paradox, by the alignment
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.96,1:07:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,of the fallacious and the imaginary
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.96,1:07:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,with the true, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.96,1:07:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty soon you'll laugh at it, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.76,1:07:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.92,1:07:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.44,1:08:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It is so cute, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.19,1:08:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.28,1:08:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so nice to come visiting again.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.28,1:08:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.28,1:08:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question from
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.67,1:08:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.67,1:08:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You talked about ego death
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.67,1:08:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and your ego death.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.67,1:08:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I have a question about
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.67,1:08:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,ego death.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.67,1:08:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.67,1:08:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.67,1:08:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Your ego death.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.67,1:08:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my ego?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.67,1:08:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, because reading the books
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.67,1:08:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I got confused.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.67,1:08:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounded like it died twice.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.67,1:08:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The question is, you talked about
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.67,1:08:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,when you were in the pits of hell
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.67,1:08:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and you were murdered,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.67,1:08:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but then you also talked about
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.67,1:08:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Rothmans, and they sound similar.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.67,1:08:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The restaurant, Rothmans?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.67,1:08:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, Rothmans, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.67,1:08:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Rothmans.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.40,1:08:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, those were different levels.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.40,1:08:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,See, as you grow up, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.40,1:08:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you experience
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.40,1:09:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,different levels.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.43,1:09:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't like you go from this
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.43,1:09:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,to that as a total completion.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.43,1:09:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't be able to handle that.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.43,1:09:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The nervous system wouldn't handle it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.68,1:09:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You move until you see,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.68,1:09:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,as I reported to the group,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.68,1:09:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the trap of the void.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.68,1:09:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Not trap, but the fallout of the void.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.68,1:09:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The void's at 850.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.84,1:09:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that's pretty impressive.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.48,1:09:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But it isn't the ultimate way.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.48,1:09:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.84,1:09:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,at various levels you experience
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.84,1:09:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the flow of the kundalini energy
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.84,1:09:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and you experience
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.84,1:09:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the bliss at 600,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.93,1:09:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,which, if the body moves
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.93,1:09:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,or doesn't move or breathes again,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.93,1:09:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,it's irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.22,1:09:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So each level is what it is
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.22,1:09:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can't compare levels.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.22,1:09:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.37,1:09:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So, from the pits of hell
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.37,1:09:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and then that's when your ego died.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.37,1:09:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You surrendered completely.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.37,1:09:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Your ego death was in that
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.37,1:10:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,event.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.13,1:10:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.52,1:10:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It was out of the pits of hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.52,1:10:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And you were an atheist before that?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.12,1:10:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.12,1:10:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,By an atheist,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.12,1:10:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,you meant you didn't believe in God
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.12,1:10:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and this guy and that guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.12,1:10:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But what did you mean by atheism?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.12,1:10:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not an atheist.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.16,1:10:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.16,1:10:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were meditating, like,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.16,1:10:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,twice a day or something, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.16,1:10:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that was a different time period.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.16,1:10:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're mixing time periods.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.16,1:10:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget, I've been around
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.16,1:10:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,close to 80 years, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.16,1:10:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's a period of 10 years of this
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.16,1:10:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and 10 years of that, 20 years of this.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.54,1:10:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,By my age, you can live decades
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.54,1:10:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,at various levels.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.54,1:10:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Decades.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.54,1:10:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that gives hope to most anyone then.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.54,1:10:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.54,1:10:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You can pull in what has to be
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.54,1:10:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,gone through.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.54,1:10:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All that stands between you and enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.67,1:10:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,now gets summoned up.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.67,1:10:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And all the lifetimes and all the karmic propensities.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.67,1:10:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And just after you got everything all cleared,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.67,1:11:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you just undid the negative karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.67,1:11:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Something in the positive side comes through
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.67,1:11:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and this may bring up
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.67,1:11:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,another karmic propensity.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.28,1:11:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're clearing out the whole stack.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.28,1:11:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.28,1:11:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A little surprise package?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.28,1:11:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it sounded like you were
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.28,1:11:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,like you might have been born
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.28,1:11:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,at least.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.28,1:11:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.28,1:11:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you what it was at age 3.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.28,1:11:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I came out of nothingness, void,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.28,1:11:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,lifetimes,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.28,1:11:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,a pathway of negation.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.28,1:11:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The ultimate reality was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.28,1:11:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.28,1:11:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Total voidness.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.20,1:11:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And I came out of that at age 3.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.20,1:11:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.20,1:11:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Into the realization of existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.20,1:11:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Which was shocking.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.55,1:11:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Not pleasing.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.55,1:11:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Like coming out of
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.71,1:11:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the safety of
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.90,1:11:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,equanimity and
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.54,1:11:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,anonymity into somethingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.54,1:11:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,As somethingness now.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.54,1:12:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stop, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.80,1:12:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a something, then you can also become a nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.80,1:12:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So, out of
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.31,1:12:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the void of
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.31,1:12:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,non-existence, nothingness
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.31,1:12:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,was the shock of existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.53,1:12:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like you've lived
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.53,1:12:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,forever in a dark cave and
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.63,1:12:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly somebody threw on Klieg lights.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.63,1:12:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It was shocking
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.88,1:12:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and not pleasant.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.98,1:12:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.98,1:12:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,there was this physicality
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.98,1:12:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,sitting in the little wagon.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.98,1:12:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The goddamn little body
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.98,1:12:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,went with this deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.52,1:12:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Which again was not pleasing.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.91,1:12:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No sooner was there
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.28,1:12:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the shocking of awareness of existence
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.28,1:12:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,that then its alternative
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.89,1:12:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,came up.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.12,1:12:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If it had come about that I had
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.12,1:12:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,come into beingness and existence,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.12,1:12:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,then it might have come about
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.21,1:12:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,hypothetically, theoretically,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.21,1:12:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,at least to not have come into existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.21,1:13:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.21,1:13:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the fear of non-existence arose.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.21,1:13:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If you picture yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.16,1:13:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,as existing,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.16,1:13:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,now it brings up the corollary.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.16,1:13:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, what about non-existence
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.26,1:13:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,as a possibility?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.26,1:13:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, that's a falsity.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.26,1:13:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's only a falsity at 850.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.41,1:13:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a falsity at 700.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.41,1:13:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not your problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.41,1:13:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But at 850, you're now accountable for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.69,1:13:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,To resolve that duality.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.69,1:13:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that an explanation? Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.84,1:13:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really good.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.09,1:13:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It might take me a while.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.50,1:13:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you never know when.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.50,1:13:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,See, the ultimate experience
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.24,1:13:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,is the absolute allness.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.24,1:13:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The allness.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.91,1:13:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So I had to back off from that,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.91,1:13:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,spend almost a lifetime
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.00,1:13:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,to transcend that error.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.93,1:13:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the ultimate state
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.93,1:13:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,is one of allness, totality,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.93,1:14:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,all inclusiveness,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.93,1:14:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and the most telling
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.96,1:14:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,difference in quality
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.00,1:14:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,between nothingness and allness
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.00,1:14:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is in allness,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.00,1:14:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the presence of the love of God
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.00,1:14:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,is overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.09,1:14:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,In voidness,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.09,1:14:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,which is very, very impressive,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.09,1:14:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,don't get me wrong,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.09,1:14:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,it is very impressive,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.28,1:14:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,it is an ultimate state.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.28,1:14:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And many people conclude that is it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.04,1:14:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Except, I'd had the experience
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.04,1:14:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,earlier in life of experiencing the presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.68,1:14:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.68,1:14:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in the nothingness of voidness,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.68,1:14:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a quality,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.68,1:14:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,an absent, a non-linear quality.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.88,1:14:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is the presence of divine love,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.88,1:14:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,which is a meltingness,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.88,1:14:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,exquisite,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.55,1:14:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,infinitely powered by virtue
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.55,1:14:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,of its exquisite nature.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.58,1:14:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was missing.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.58,1:14:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.58,1:14:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,one thought remained.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.21,1:15:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And it took me all the energy
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.21,1:15:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I could summon up over the hours
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.21,1:15:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,to energize that thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.79,1:15:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And even then to energize
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.79,1:15:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,being attracted to that thought
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.79,1:15:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to back out of the void.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.42,1:15:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I managed to attach
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.42,1:15:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,a sense of reality
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.42,1:15:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to a linearity.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.42,1:15:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.28,1:15:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew that thought was my only way out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.79,1:15:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I needed a thought to get out of nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.79,1:15:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There ain't any thoughts in nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.79,1:15:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite a problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.20,1:15:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're looking for what to hang onto,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.20,1:15:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,there's nothing to hang onto.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.20,1:15:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a non-linear volition.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.78,1:15:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The decision
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.88,1:15:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to align one's life with God,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.88,1:15:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to surrender it all to divinity,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.88,1:15:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,had brought in
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.91,1:15:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,a karmic...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.04,1:15:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I see it now.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.04,1:15:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a karmic consequence of that
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.04,1:16:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that allowed me to have the one thought
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.04,1:16:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,for it to still be in the void.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.86,1:16:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.50,1:16:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a very sophisticated question.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.50,1:16:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's one thought that brought you out of hell too.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.04,1:16:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.16,1:16:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And you didn't go for the void then?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.16,1:16:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that was the opposite direction of the void.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.16,1:16:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I could have used the little void there.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.16,1:16:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What time do we have to quit?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.16,1:16:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.89,1:16:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be done just in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.89,1:16:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It always finishes just in time.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.89,1:16:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, I have two questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.89,1:16:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,One question is,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.89,1:16:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,you mentioned that the consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.89,1:16:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,of the world increased
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.89,1:16:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,in the late 80's to 205.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.89,1:16:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And last year
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.89,1:16:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to 207.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.89,1:16:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And the question I had then was
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.89,1:16:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,why do you think that's so?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.89,1:16:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrated as so.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.89,1:16:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And the second question is,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.89,1:16:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.89,1:16:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't know if this is in fact
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.89,1:16:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,truth or not truth,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.89,1:17:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,of indigo and crystal children
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.89,1:17:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,coming into the consciousness of the world
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.89,1:17:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,with the purpose of raising
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.89,1:17:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the world's consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.89,1:17:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.28,1:17:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether that's something that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.28,1:17:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It does not ring true with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.28,1:17:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's what I wanted to know.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.28,1:17:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Crystal children and indigo children
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.28,1:17:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,would have to calibrate way, way up
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.28,1:17:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to be raising the consciousness of all mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.28,1:17:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I think what they really mean is that
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.28,1:17:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,they would have to calibrate
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.28,1:17:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the consciousness of all to see them differently.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.28,1:17:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.28,1:17:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And thereby raise the consciousness level of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.28,1:17:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think the world,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.28,1:17:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the consciousness has gone up since the 190's?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.28,1:17:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the province of divinity, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.28,1:17:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You can ask God when you get there,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.28,1:17:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,how come?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.28,1:17:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.28,1:17:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I think because
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.28,1:17:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the evolution of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.34,1:17:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,if we ask
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.34,1:17:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,by, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.34,1:17:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is it intrinsic
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.34,1:17:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the consciousness itself
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.34,1:18:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to evolve and seek its own source?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.34,1:18:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.92,1:18:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that over there.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.92,1:18:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That is so, it is intrinsic.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.92,1:18:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's intrinsic to the quality of consciousness itself
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.92,1:18:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to grow and seek
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.92,1:18:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,its, to return to its source.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.92,1:18:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So we then
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.46,1:18:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,look forward to...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.46,1:18:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It negates any negation.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.49,1:18:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Increasing consciousness over time.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.49,1:18:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It happens of its own nature.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.72,1:18:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And you get swept along with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.48,1:18:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody ever asked an octopus
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.29,1:18:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,if it wants to get smarter.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.80,1:18:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody even consulted me, he says.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.80,1:18:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody ever consulted me on the issue.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.80,1:18:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.03,1:18:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.09,1:18:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I teach Reiki.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.09,1:18:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.09,1:18:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,up until noon today
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.09,1:18:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have listed that as an asset
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.09,1:18:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,of mine. But some of your
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.09,1:18:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,remarks, which I can't
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.09,1:18:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,perfectly remember,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.09,1:18:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,kind of threw me.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.09,1:19:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I'm
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.09,1:19:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,wondering what to make of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.09,1:19:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it isn't discipline.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.09,1:19:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the misuse of the discipline.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.09,1:19:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't negate the value of discipline.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.09,1:19:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the business
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.09,1:19:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,of channeling? Because
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.09,1:19:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,as I'm told... I already told you what I think.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.09,1:19:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.09,1:19:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you how it
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.09,1:19:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,arose. I told you what
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.09,1:19:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the error is. And you have to
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.09,1:19:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of think about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.09,1:19:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Each of those things
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.09,1:19:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, is not positive
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.54,1:19:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,or negative in itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.67,1:19:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Because such things are
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.67,1:19:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,a necessary experience as part of
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.67,1:19:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual evolution. You know.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.37,1:19:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Part of spiritual evolution
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.95,1:19:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,is you sort of get bit by the bug.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.95,1:19:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you start to explore everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.95,1:19:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You go to every consciousness festival
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.95,1:19:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.95,1:19:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual bazaar and
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.95,1:19:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,New Age festival.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.95,1:19:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.95,1:19:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,aisle after aisle of exhibits
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.95,1:20:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and parades and flashing lights and
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.95,1:20:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,smells and incenses and massages
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.95,1:20:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and balancings. And it's
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.17,1:20:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,a whole area to explore.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.17,1:20:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing wrong with exploring it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.43,1:20:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you know what it is unless you check it out?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.43,1:20:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.49,1:20:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Check it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.49,1:20:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think though that if she is a
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.49,1:20:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,practicing Reiki, is the intention
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.49,1:20:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,behind her to heal that person?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.49,1:20:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course the intention is what gives it the power.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.49,1:20:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're correct. So it's not
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.49,1:20:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,magic. So, sometimes
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.49,1:20:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,it gets caught in magic, then it gets
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.49,1:20:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,commercialized, etc.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.49,1:20:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really aware of the commercialization
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.49,1:20:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and dislike it enormously.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.49,1:20:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was just wondering if this
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.49,1:20:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,was something that I should continue
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.49,1:20:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,doing because I see that as being
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.49,1:20:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,giving. Well, it depends on what it means
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.49,1:20:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,to you and the part it plays in your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.49,1:20:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So, another thing, you become
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.49,1:20:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,enthusiast to various things along the way
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.49,1:20:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you outgrow them. See?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.49,1:20:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think the power
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.49,1:20:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,of Reiki is the intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.49,1:20:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The intense intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.32,1:21:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the energy summoned forth by that
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.32,1:21:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,intention. You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.39,1:21:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I would take it out of the realm of magic.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.39,1:21:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the only trouble with a lot of new age kind of
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.39,1:21:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,things is they really are
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.39,1:21:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,contextualized as a certain kind of magic.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.39,1:21:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Not for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.39,1:21:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.39,1:21:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I was concerned about...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.39,1:21:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The conscious utilization of energies
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.39,1:21:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,for a benign purpose. So, the intention
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.39,1:21:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,is very vigorous.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.00,1:21:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, because I don't support something, it doesn't
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.00,1:21:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,mean I oppose it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.56,1:21:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I support vanilla, but that doesn't mean
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.56,1:21:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm against chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.56,1:21:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.72,1:21:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any advice for someone who is
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.72,1:21:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,dealing with ADD?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.72,1:21:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,ADD?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.72,1:21:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you believe in it?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.72,1:21:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think it's an impediment to awareness?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.72,1:21:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've treated hundreds and hundreds of cases.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.72,1:21:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What is ADD? Attention Deficit Disorder.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.72,1:21:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.39,1:22:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It causes impairment and suffering.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.39,1:22:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Impairment of functioning.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.39,1:22:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This creates a social
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.39,1:22:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,kickback, which may decrease the
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.39,1:22:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,person's self-esteem.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.39,1:22:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And the net result may be
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.00,1:22:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,primarily the loss of self-esteem
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.00,1:22:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't keep up.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.00,1:22:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always getting D's.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.03,1:22:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always putting the dunce hat on.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.03,1:22:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always being the imbecile.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.03,1:22:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always being ridiculed.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.03,1:22:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So the punishment, the punitive reaction of society
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.03,1:22:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to the disorder, unless it's corrected,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.03,1:22:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,is often worse than the disorder.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.96,1:22:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, so what if you can't concentrate
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.34,1:22:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can't read?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.98,1:22:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.98,1:22:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,In a society in which this is a necessity,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.98,1:22:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,now you're at an impasse.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.08,1:22:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I would say if a thing can be cured
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.08,1:22:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,by a simple medication,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.08,1:22:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see no reason why not.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.08,1:22:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The Course in Miracles
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.33,1:22:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and everybody else says,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.33,1:22:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,all things are physical, mental, and spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.36,1:22:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's arrogant to deny any one of the three.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.36,1:22:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So I would say,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.62,1:22:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,if you've got ADD, you do all you can
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.62,1:23:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,behaviorally, medically,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.13,1:23:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritually.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.13,1:23:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The same as any other disorder.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.51,1:23:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A duodenal ulcer,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.51,1:23:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,ADHD, you do the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.51,1:23:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.88,1:23:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I take things for something,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.21,1:23:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,so what?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.98,1:23:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you, Dr.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.00,1:23:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to convert styrofoam back into bone.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.00,1:23:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I mean, that requires,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.00,1:23:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,you've got to put something in your nose.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.41,1:23:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And now it pulls calcium,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.41,1:23:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's a wonderment, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.41,1:23:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So you do that, you also pray,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.41,1:23:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and you also be careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.57,1:23:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I had a question about,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.57,1:23:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,as students on the path to enlightenment,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.57,1:23:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,we have the responsibility of walking the path
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.57,1:23:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,as straight as possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.57,1:23:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But when we're married, we have family,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.57,1:23:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and sometimes we tend to maybe
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.57,1:24:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,fall to the wayside,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.57,1:24:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,embroiled in the problems of those loved ones.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.57,1:24:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And how to,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.57,1:24:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,how do we walk that line?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.57,1:24:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to set it aside and compartmentalize it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.57,1:24:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is spiritual,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.57,1:24:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and this is daily life.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.57,1:24:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What you do is spiritualize your daily life.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.57,1:24:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason you're peeling potatoes
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.57,1:24:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is being of service
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.57,1:24:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,to life in the form of this family, etc.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.57,1:24:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you do is spiritualize
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.57,1:24:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,your endeavors, so that you
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.57,1:24:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,contextualize them differently.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.57,1:24:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is spiritual,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.57,1:24:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and this is family, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.57,1:24:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I argue for the sake of my family.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.57,1:24:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.57,1:24:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you arguing for the sake of your family?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.57,1:24:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you esteem it,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.57,1:24:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,because you are dedicated to its well-being.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.57,1:24:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So spiritualize what you do,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.57,1:24:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and recontextualize it,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.57,1:24:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and you'll see everything you do is spiritual
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.57,1:24:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,if you contextualize it in such a way.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.57,1:24:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything you're doing is karma yoga
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.57,1:24:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,for the sake of your family.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.57,1:24:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I got that karma yoga part earlier.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.57,1:24:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm making the lunches for my kids,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.57,1:24:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm making the karma yoga.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.57,1:25:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,See, the maternal was the avenue
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.57,1:25:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,by which love entered the human domain.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.57,1:25:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There wasn't any love before the maternal.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.57,1:25:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Males do not love each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.57,1:25:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Not early in the game.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.57,1:25:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Only later, only later in evolution.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.57,1:25:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's after the maternal
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.57,1:25:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,has already brought forth
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.57,1:25:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,love as a prevailing energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.57,1:25:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The first time the man experiences it
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.57,1:25:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,is via the mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.60,1:25:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.60,1:25:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.35,1:25:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.35,1:25:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is in regard to self-inquiry.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.35,1:25:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,In your book, you say that
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.35,1:25:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the question,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.35,1:25:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,how is it that I am aware
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.35,1:25:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,or even know that I exist
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.41,1:25:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,is a question that would lead you
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.41,1:25:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,all the way to the door,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.41,1:25:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,or one of the only questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.41,1:25:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was curious if you could kind of elaborate on that,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.41,1:25:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and if I'm supposed to ask that
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.41,1:26:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,as kind of like a form of prayer to God,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.64,1:26:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,for God to show me that,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.64,1:26:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,well, it's moving,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.64,1:26:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe it's better to move from who I am
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.64,1:26:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to what I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.64,1:26:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramana Maharshi apparently,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.64,1:26:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I think,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.64,1:26:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,favored that.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.64,1:26:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-inquiry?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.15,1:26:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Who am I is already self-limiting
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.15,1:26:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,because the who is a linearity.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.15,1:26:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The what you are is a quality.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.47,1:26:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you experience the reality of the self,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.47,1:26:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,it is not a who.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.47,1:26:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a what.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.72,1:26:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a quality.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.72,1:26:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pervasive,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.85,1:26:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,self-existent quality.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.85,1:26:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best to wonder who,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.07,1:26:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,not who I am,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.07,1:26:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but what am I.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.16,1:26:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Because what is it that asks who am I?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.57,1:26:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.57,1:26:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So you go back to the asker of the question,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.57,1:26:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're already out of the trap of the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.57,1:26:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.57,1:26:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Because
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.60,1:26:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,what you are
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.86,1:27:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is not a who, but a what.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.55,1:27:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.12,1:27:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,With apologies to Ramana.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.67,1:27:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.34,1:27:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.34,1:27:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.34,1:27:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not exactly sure how to format this,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.34,1:27:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but you had talked about the calibration
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.34,1:27:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,of the United States being 420.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.34,1:27:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,421.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.34,1:27:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And you've also talked about
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.34,1:27:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,how in advertising
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.34,1:27:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you project to the audience
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.34,1:27:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're trying to communicate with
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.34,1:27:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and the other countries I know
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.34,1:27:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,ranked at different levels of calibration.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.34,1:27:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it that
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.34,1:27:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the United States can calibrate
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.34,1:27:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,420,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.34,1:27:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet their methodology with dealing with
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.34,1:27:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,not only its own citizens,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.34,1:27:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but people of the world,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.34,1:27:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a judgment.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.34,1:27:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a judgment you're making.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.34,1:27:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your perception.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.34,1:28:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no idea what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.20,1:28:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to calibrate
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.20,1:28:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the level of all the members of the cabinet,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.65,1:28:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the supreme court,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.65,1:28:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,federal court, state court, judicial,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.68,1:28:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrate the ninth court,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.55,1:28:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,circuit court of appeals,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.64,1:28:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrate all the leading people,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.03,1:28:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrate the speaking voices
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.03,1:28:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,of politics.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.16,1:28:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you can lay it out on a map
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.16,1:28:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and you begin to see
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.16,1:28:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,an alignment of how
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.92,1:28:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that prevails.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.92,1:28:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Because each is an expression
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.15,1:28:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,of a certain level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.15,1:28:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a matter
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.15,1:28:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,of being right or wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.15,1:28:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a matter of being right or wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.91,1:28:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess, though,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.12,1:28:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,when the President comes to the United States
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.12,1:28:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,or when he speaks to his people
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.12,1:28:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and the whole level
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.12,1:28:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,of the fear level,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.12,1:28:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,it seemed like
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.12,1:28:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the way of getting the people
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.12,1:28:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,behind him
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.12,1:29:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,was through fear,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.12,1:29:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,which is a lower calibrated energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.12,1:29:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand what you're saying
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.12,1:29:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that you need to calibrate the individuals.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.12,1:29:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I do understand that.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.12,1:29:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,When he tells you
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.12,1:29:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,a reality that threatens your existence,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.12,1:29:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the fear is
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.32,1:29:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,your idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.14,1:29:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go off the highway, you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.14,1:29:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I say that to make fear?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.14,1:29:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, that's why we want guardrails.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.14,1:29:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,See,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.45,1:29:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot be responsible
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.45,1:29:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,for your decision
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.45,1:29:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,of how you want to emotionally react.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.61,1:29:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not creating fear.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.61,1:29:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're creating the fear.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.87,1:29:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How you individually perceive
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.67,1:29:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,his message, but he also
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.67,1:29:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,perceives as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.67,1:29:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.67,1:29:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,it's his responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.67,1:29:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we said
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.53,1:29:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,to not know that there was
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.53,1:29:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,500,000
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.53,1:29:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinese communist soldiers
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.53,1:30:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,north of the border in Korea
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.53,1:30:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,was a gross
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.53,1:30:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,dereliction of dirty duty.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.53,1:30:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If I ask you what does that calibrate,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.53,1:30:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll see it's about 180.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.53,1:30:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You want a surgeon that operates on you
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.53,1:30:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,at 180?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.14,1:30:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.14,1:30:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Integrity means
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.14,1:30:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that you must fulfill the obligation
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.14,1:30:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,of your office.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.14,1:30:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,As a physician, I tell people
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.14,1:30:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you take this, you get better.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.14,1:30:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't take it, you probably get a heart attack and die.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.14,1:30:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not to create fear.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.14,1:30:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just telling them what the facts are.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.14,1:30:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My obligation is
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.36,1:30:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to my role.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.36,1:30:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to be afraid of what I said,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.90,1:30:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that's your option.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.32,1:30:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not trying to control
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.32,1:30:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,whether they take it or not
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.32,1:30:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,with fear.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.32,1:30:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not my intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.34,1:30:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If I take the medicine, the bones get stronger.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.34,1:30:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.60,1:30:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,you can get what's called
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.60,1:30:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,fracture.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.17,1:31:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's a fracture
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.17,1:31:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stress fracture, they call it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.17,1:31:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I said,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.17,1:31:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,do I have to put this stuff in my nose
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.17,1:31:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and take this crap and all?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.17,1:31:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, well if you don't, you can be walking along
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.17,1:31:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and your femur will just go crunch.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.17,1:31:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, well that's inconvenient
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.62,1:31:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,as all hell when I'm about to get on the bus.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.62,1:31:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really want it to go crunch
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.62,1:31:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,all by itself out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.62,1:31:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So I take the sniffer.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.62,1:31:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's not controlling me with fear.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.62,1:31:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.62,1:31:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,understand your point.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.62,1:31:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But if somebody,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.62,1:31:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say you calibrated somebody
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.62,1:31:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that's making decisions like that
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.62,1:31:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that affect the rest of the world
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.62,1:31:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and they calibrate at 420, 421,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.62,1:31:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.62,1:31:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of integrity
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.62,1:31:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,for themselves
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.62,1:31:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and where they're calibrating,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.62,1:31:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,don't they have the responsibility
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.62,1:31:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,to make integrity based
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.62,1:31:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,decisions that affect others?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.62,1:31:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever they consider
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.62,1:31:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,their role
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.62,1:32:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and integrity is their role.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.62,1:32:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're the mother
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.62,1:32:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and the water's contaminated
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.62,1:32:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and you tell them you drink that
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.72,1:32:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll be dysentery and die.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.72,1:32:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your role as a mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.58,1:32:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're children
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.58,1:32:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're your wards
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.77,1:32:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,is now your obligation to prevent them
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.77,1:32:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,from drinking the water
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.77,1:32:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,until they're smart enough
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.67,1:32:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to not drink it themselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.67,1:32:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Also they don't have the strength
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.67,1:32:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to protect themselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.63,1:32:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So as mother
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.63,1:32:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,in their behalf.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.63,1:32:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.45,1:32:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.38,1:32:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to read the oath of office.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.38,1:32:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll tell you
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.34,1:32:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,he took the oath of office.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.60,1:32:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.77,1:32:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well they don't understand triage.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.77,1:32:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Triage you don't understand
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.77,1:33:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,until consciousness level 390.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.77,1:33:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody in power is often
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.77,1:33:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,between a rock and a hard place.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.77,1:33:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's gonna be
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.93,1:33:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,vilified whichever way he goes.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.93,1:33:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't kill
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.41,1:33:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,480,000
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.41,1:33:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,or 180,000
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.41,1:33:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,or whatever Hiroshima was
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.41,1:33:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,180,000 voluntarily
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.41,1:33:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you're gonna kill
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.54,1:33:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,7 million involuntarily.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.12,1:33:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So the rock and the hard place
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.12,1:33:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,of Truman
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.12,1:33:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and I calibrated his decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.12,1:33:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,His decision was at 485.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.12,1:33:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to have been in the military
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.39,1:33:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,to understand triage.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.39,1:33:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll tell you when I was in the fleet
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.39,1:33:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,if you went over
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.39,1:33:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,to get you
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.39,1:33:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I went over the side
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.70,1:33:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,swept between two ships
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.70,1:33:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,a steel cable almost snapped me in half
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.70,1:33:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,it just missed my head
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.70,1:33:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,it would have beheaded me.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.99,1:33:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huge force. As this ship went up
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.99,1:34:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the steel cable went like a shot
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.02,1:34:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,like a cannon.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.24,1:34:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It would have cut me right in half.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.52,1:34:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So I fell off the buoy
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.52,1:34:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,into the Huangpu River.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.68,1:34:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ganges is awful.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.68,1:34:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You fight your way between
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.68,1:34:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the feces and the dead bodies
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.68,1:34:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and the current is fantastic
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.68,1:34:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and it takes you
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.68,1:34:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and here I'm headed for a nest of ships
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.68,1:34:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,destroyers and sudden destroyers
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.68,1:34:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,fast little ships
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.68,1:34:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway they're smashing
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.68,1:34:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,against each other
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.68,1:34:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,this one is smashing against each other
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.68,1:34:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and these huge things are smashing
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.68,1:34:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm floating right for them
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.68,1:34:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,all 110 pounds
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.93,1:34:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,flailing in the water
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.44,1:34:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and to help me
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.73,1:34:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,not only did I get off the buoy
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.73,1:34:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,before it would have cut my head off
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.73,1:34:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the next thing is I'm floating
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.73,1:34:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and I got floated right up to the very prow of this ship
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.73,1:34:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,like this
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.80,1:35:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the Huangpu River current is going by
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.80,1:35:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,dead bodies are
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.80,1:35:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,oh sorry going by
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.80,1:35:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,we have to get them off
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.80,1:35:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,we need them off
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.80,1:35:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,there's the river now
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.80,1:35:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.80,1:35:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,what do we got for a mop?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.80,1:35:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,anything?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.63,1:35:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,moppity moppity mop
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.78,1:35:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,well we become part and parcel of our message don't we
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.78,1:35:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.16,1:35:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot what I was telling you about that
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.16,1:35:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the water
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.16,1:35:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,it had to do with karma
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.16,1:35:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.16,1:35:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,so actually I got hung up there
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.16,1:35:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,like this
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.48,1:35:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and they had to come out and rescue me
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.48,1:35:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,so I wasn't too great in the navy
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.48,1:35:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,they had to rescue me from the top of the mast
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.48,1:35:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,because I froze up there with fear
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.48,1:35:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,they had me as a deep sea diver
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.48,1:35:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and they put this bell over my head
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.48,1:35:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and the minute I got below water
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.48,1:35:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I got hyperventilation
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.48,1:36:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn't stop breathing
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.24,1:36:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,as a mesomorph I was a failure
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.24,1:36:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you that
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.40,1:36:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you very much Dr. Hawkins
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.40,1:36:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you honor me and we're all very fortunate
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.40,1:36:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you Susan
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.26,1:36:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you started this lecture saying
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.26,1:36:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to make your life a mudra
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.26,1:36:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to be one with the
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.26,1:36:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,absolute field
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.26,1:36:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and I realized that
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.45,1:36:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,when this physicality that we call
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.45,1:36:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins speaks
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.45,1:36:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and is trying to elucidate
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.45,1:36:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,this concept
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.68,1:36:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,very little
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.70,1:36:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,reference is made to the I
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.70,1:36:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and you speak in a very non-dualistic way
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.70,1:36:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,would it
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.08,1:36:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,improve our chances
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.08,1:36:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,help us in any way as a spiritual practice
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.08,1:36:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to try to
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.08,1:36:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,speak this way
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.08,1:36:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and not use the subject predicate form of language
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.08,1:36:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,which is in itself dualistic
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.08,1:36:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought of that
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.08,1:36:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you're correct
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.08,1:37:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I always explain things
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.08,1:37:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of in the third person
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.08,1:37:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.23,1:37:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,because I would witness the body
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.23,1:37:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,getting up and doing something
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.23,1:37:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and ordinarily you would say I
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.23,1:37:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,it's sort of the detached witness
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.86,1:37:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're the witness
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.86,1:37:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,of the phenomena
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.24,1:37:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I never noticed that
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.24,1:37:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's a fact
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.84,1:37:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't language it
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.84,1:37:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,as a subject predicate
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.84,1:37:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,for an object
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.84,1:37:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,like who is this doing that
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.84,1:37:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,it's more or less I guess
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.84,1:37:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,what in language you would call the passive third person
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.88,1:37:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,or the passive third
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.64,1:37:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,in writing I forget what they call it
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.64,1:37:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,besides confusing
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.21,1:37:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the passive third person
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.21,1:37:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't that what it is
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.21,1:37:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the passive third person
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.21,1:37:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,where you describe the phenomena
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.21,1:37:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,as the passage of equalities
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.21,1:37:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and not necessarily a personal intervention
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.21,1:38:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you would say
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.21,1:38:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that's typical of scientific writing too
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.50,1:38:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,right
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.50,1:38:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,sulfur were put in
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.50,1:38:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,with one sniff of potassium
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.50,1:38:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and bright lights evolved
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.50,1:38:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,so would it benefit us
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.50,1:38:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to do that
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.50,1:38:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought of it
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.69,1:38:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,as a tool or useful tool
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.69,1:38:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,it may well be
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.85,1:38:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,because I kind of surmised that
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.85,1:38:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,from my readings in the past
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.85,1:38:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you suggest
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.85,1:38:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,we have permission to ask it now
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.16,1:38:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you suggest
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.77,1:38:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,we have permission to ask it now
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.77,1:38:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,we got no permission
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.77,1:38:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,one other thing then
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.77,1:38:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,below the level of 200
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.77,1:38:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,they act in concordance
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.77,1:38:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,with an attractor field
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.77,1:38:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and have no personal karma
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.77,1:38:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and thereby have no personal choice
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.77,1:38:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,then how do they take the leap
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.77,1:38:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond 200
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.77,1:38:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,perhaps the evolution
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.77,1:38:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,of the field itself
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.77,1:38:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,in other words the fields themselves
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.77,1:39:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you see the progression of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.77,1:39:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,so progression
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.77,1:39:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness tends to
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.77,1:39:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,evolve into greater and greater
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.77,1:39:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,complexity and then beyond
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.77,1:39:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,complexity to simplicity
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.77,1:39:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to return to its source
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.44,1:39:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,it could be the impersonal
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.44,1:39:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,consequence of the karma
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.99,1:39:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,there are many ancient references
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.99,1:39:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,to it they're not my personal experience
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.99,1:39:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,so I can't say
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.99,1:39:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,the Rig Veda says
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.99,1:39:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that each thing by virtue of what it is
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.60,1:39:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,subserves higher life
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.88,1:39:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and by subserving higher life
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.88,1:39:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it earns the karmic
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.88,1:39:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,right to become the higher life
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.92,1:39:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.11,1:39:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the lower life
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.72,1:39:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,which it surrenders itself
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.48,1:39:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to be eaten by you
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.48,1:39:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't see it
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.32,1:39:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,but it gives up its life
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.41,1:39:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,to God
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.54,1:39:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and then
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.85,1:39:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,comes forth its human energy
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.85,1:40:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and now has earned the karmic right
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.85,1:40:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to eventuate into humanness
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.92,1:40:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.85,1:40:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,you might call it
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.43,1:40:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the karma of sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.43,1:40:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,each thing surrenders its life
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.00,1:40:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to support the life
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.00,1:40:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond it or above it
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.00,1:40:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and by virtue of that earns the right
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.00,1:40:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to become that which is above it
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.00,1:40:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.64,1:40:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,we have three minutes left
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.78,1:40:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,we got just enough time for the last
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.42,1:40:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,if we're quick as a wink we'll make it
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.42,1:40:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,in the book I
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.42,1:40:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,wrote that being in the presence
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.42,1:40:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,in the aura of the enlightened teacher
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.42,1:40:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,has a karmic imprint
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.42,1:40:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,can you expound a little bit on what that means
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.42,1:40:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to the spiritual aspirant
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.61,1:40:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a frequency
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.61,1:40:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,that's transmitted in the aura
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.61,1:40:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.90,1:40:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,in going into the state that occurred
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.90,1:40:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,in this lifetime
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.90,1:41:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,or undoubtedly the consequence of the energy
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.90,1:41:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,picked up prior
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.90,1:41:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,because in walking
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.90,1:41:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,through the final door
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.41,1:41:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,which was terrifying
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.41,1:41:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and agonizing
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.41,1:41:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,for a few moments
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.60,1:41:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,there was the knowingness
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.83,1:41:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,with absolute certainty
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.83,1:41:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,walk through all fear
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.17,1:41:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,all fear is illusion
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.17,1:41:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that came as a powerful certainty
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.17,1:41:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,concrete knowingness
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.17,1:41:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and that
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.19,1:41:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,enabled the surrender
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.19,1:41:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,where did it come from
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.19,1:41:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,because there's no memory there
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.19,1:41:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,at that level your mind is silent
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.70,1:41:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you think when I get there I'm going to remember it
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.70,1:41:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not going to remember it
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.70,1:41:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,there's nobody there to remember it
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.70,1:41:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no memory you can send forth
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.70,1:41:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no thinkingness or thought or mind
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.82,1:41:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the knowingness
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.82,1:41:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,so like the vibration is waiting for you
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.81,1:41:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and when you need it
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.81,1:41:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the vibration is like an encoded message
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.81,1:42:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and the encoding opens up
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.81,1:42:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,as the knowingness of the presence
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.81,1:42:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore it can only be transmitted
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.00,1:42:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,by those who have done it
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.00,1:42:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,it has to be somebody who has actually
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.42,1:42:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,done it
Dialogue: 0,1:42:12.80,1:42:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you can see
Dialogue: 0,1:42:15.06,1:42:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I will tell you
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.06,1:42:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,when you surrender your life to divinity
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.67,1:42:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you will die
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.67,1:42:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and be born
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.50,1:42:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a fact
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.53,1:42:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that you will die
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.36,1:42:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the only death you can experience
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.48,1:42:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and those are the doors that open
Dialogue: 0,1:42:34.48,1:42:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,what is beyond
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.48,1:42:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is beyond all description
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.92,1:42:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,so the knowingness
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.20,1:42:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,having heard it as the frequency
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.20,1:42:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and the vibration is now recorded
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.20,1:42:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,in the field of consciousness forever
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.84,1:42:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,likewise am I responsible
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.84,1:42:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,karmically for having said it
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.84,1:42:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's only with full awareness
Dialogue: 0,1:42:57.22,1:43:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that I even say it
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.72,1:43:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.82,1:43:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,first of all
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.27,1:43:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to say I have tremendous
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.27,1:43:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,gratitude for the
Dialogue: 0,1:43:17.68,1:43:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual guidance and awareness
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.68,1:43:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that your consciousness brings to us
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.68,1:43:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,through your books
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.68,1:43:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just amazing
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.68,1:43:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but my question has to do with health
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.68,1:43:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and I know you've written that historically
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.68,1:43:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you had a plethora of health problems
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.68,1:43:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that you went through
Dialogue: 0,1:43:33.68,1:43:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm struggling
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.68,1:43:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,with a few things myself
Dialogue: 0,1:43:37.68,1:43:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,they come and they go
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.68,1:43:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,spent many thousands of dollars
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.68,1:43:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and still have it
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.68,1:43:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,still stuck with it
Dialogue: 0,1:43:45.68,1:43:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,somehow I'm myself in this conundrum
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.68,1:43:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,don't quite know how to get myself out
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.68,1:43:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,of it
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.68,1:43:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter how much money you spend on it
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.68,1:43:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,it still goes its merry way
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.68,1:43:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,thousands of dollars
Dialogue: 0,1:43:57.68,1:43:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm making doctors, chiropractors, acupuncturists
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.68,1:44:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,a bunch of people rich
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.68,1:44:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm still struggling
Dialogue: 0,1:44:03.68,1:44:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really drawn to what you had said
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.68,1:44:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you mean struggle
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.68,1:44:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,why struggle
Dialogue: 0,1:44:15.06,1:44:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,struggling to feel better I guess
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.06,1:44:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,struggling to feel better
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.25,1:44:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,struggling doesn't work
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.76,1:44:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't seem to be
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.76,1:44:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,surrendering
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.47,1:44:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,to resist
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.79,1:44:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that means you're holding out against it
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.03,1:44:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that would be my quick read
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.52,1:44:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,you can go through surgery
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.52,1:44:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,without anesthesia
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.54,1:44:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,so long as you don't resist
Dialogue: 0,1:44:49.54,1:44:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,so long as you stay on the edge of the razor
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.54,1:44:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the minute you get off the edge of the razor
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.08,1:44:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,agony
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.63,1:44:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.91,1:45:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I would let go resisting it
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.91,1:45:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,if the bones turn to styrofoam
Dialogue: 0,1:45:05.48,1:45:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and collapse
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.48,1:45:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,well then you're a pile of stuff
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.48,1:45:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.24,1:45:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,in the meantime you do what you can
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.24,1:45:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,in the practical level
Dialogue: 0,1:45:17.65,1:45:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,so you can keep riding out there
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.65,1:45:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,on the range as long as possible
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.65,1:45:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I'm saying
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.61,1:45:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,what else can you do
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.31,1:45:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the ravages of age
Dialogue: 0,1:45:31.72,1:45:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that's what the Buddha said
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.10,1:45:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,sickness, old age and death
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.10,1:45:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,sickness, old age and poverty and death
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.10,1:45:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,is the karma
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.96,1:45:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,of reincarnating
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.96,1:45:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,as a linearity human
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.96,1:45:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.96,1:45:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,on the plus side it gives you another
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.96,1:45:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,shot at it
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.56,1:45:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.79,1:46:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,okay we got
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.79,1:46:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that's enough
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.04,1:46:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you got another shot at it
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.82,1:46:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going down the tubes
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.82,1:46:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,go down the tubes
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.17,1:46:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,laughing and whistling
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.17,1:46:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,namaste from Ann Arbor, Michigan
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.17,1:46:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,my name's David
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.17,1:46:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm part of David Hawking's study group
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.17,1:46:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,that meets every Thursday
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.29,1:46:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,way better than going to church
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.29,1:46:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,it's growing and we wondered
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.29,1:46:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,if you had any advice for us
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.29,1:46:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,oh Ann Arbor yeah the university area
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.29,1:46:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Fred Sauer started one group
Dialogue: 0,1:46:34.29,1:46:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and it got too big so now there's another
Dialogue: 0,1:46:36.29,1:46:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,oh yeah yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.29,1:46:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,well you do the same you do with any
Dialogue: 0,1:46:40.29,1:46:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,information of value
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.55,1:46:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,you
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.55,1:46:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,if you can calibrate
Dialogue: 0,1:46:46.55,1:46:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,do that way
Dialogue: 0,1:46:48.55,1:46:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,you calibrate the energy of
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.55,1:46:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the validity of a teaching
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.55,1:46:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and give it
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.55,1:46:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the attention that that calibration
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.55,1:46:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,deserves
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.71,1:47:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,if I get that something calibrates
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.71,1:47:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,at 700 or 800 or 900
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.71,1:47:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm probably going to give it more attention and value
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.71,1:47:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,than something at 250 but
Dialogue: 0,1:47:06.71,1:47:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,something at 250 may be
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.71,1:47:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,necessary to master before I can move
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.71,1:47:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,there so there's no point
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.71,1:47:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,in jumping the gun either
Dialogue: 0,1:47:16.44,1:47:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I say take the simplest
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.44,1:47:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,things and practice them until they
Dialogue: 0,1:47:20.44,1:47:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,become who you are
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.44,1:47:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and then the next thing will present itself
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.44,1:47:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,when you see the intrinsic beauty
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.44,1:47:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,of all that exists you see
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.79,1:47:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the intrinsic quality of divinity
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.79,1:47:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that shines forth of all things
Dialogue: 0,1:47:32.79,1:47:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the next move opens itself up
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.79,1:47:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to you see
Dialogue: 0,1:47:37.04,1:47:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,because you've asked
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.11,1:47:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,God haven't you
Dialogue: 0,1:47:41.14,1:47:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you've asked God
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.14,1:47:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that's all you got to do
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.00,1:47:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,they say when you pray for
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.51,1:47:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,rain grab a hole
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.54,1:47:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make this quick
Dialogue: 0,1:47:57.54,1:47:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,could you just say something about the power
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.54,1:48:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,of forgiveness
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.18,1:48:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,say something
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.18,1:48:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I could say a couple
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.18,1:48:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,hours about it what would you like
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.18,1:48:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,in particular
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.18,1:48:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an addictions therapist
Dialogue: 0,1:48:12.18,1:48:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an addictions therapist
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.18,1:48:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and in helping
Dialogue: 0,1:48:16.18,1:48:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,addicts forgive themselves
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.18,1:48:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,1:48:21.20,1:48:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,can you offer any help
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.20,1:48:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,in how to help them
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.20,1:48:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,forgive themselves for what being an addict
Dialogue: 0,1:48:27.30,1:48:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,or the things they did as an addict
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.30,1:48:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,or
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.59,1:48:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,if you understand the quality of addiction
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.59,1:48:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,forgiveness comes about
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.59,1:48:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,just as a consequence of
Dialogue: 0,1:48:37.59,1:48:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,of information
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.91,1:48:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,you see the brain cell will prefer
Dialogue: 0,1:48:41.91,1:48:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the substance
Dialogue: 0,1:48:43.91,1:48:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,you can raise neurons
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.91,1:48:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,cerebral neurons in a petri dish
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.91,1:48:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and gradually increase
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.91,1:48:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the level of opium in the petri
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.91,1:48:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say it was opium
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.00,1:48:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,eventually those neurons
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.00,1:48:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,will become dependent on the presence of that opium
Dialogue: 0,1:48:58.00,1:49:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and if you begin to withdraw
Dialogue: 0,1:49:00.00,1:49:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the opium from the culture media
Dialogue: 0,1:49:02.00,1:49:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the neurons will shrink up and die
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.00,1:49:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.80,1:49:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the personal self
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.80,1:49:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,has gotten addicted
Dialogue: 0,1:49:10.80,1:49:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but so has the physiologic self
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.80,1:49:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that to me is true addiction
Dialogue: 0,1:49:14.80,1:49:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,what people call addiction
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.80,1:49:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just bad habits a lot of it
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.80,1:49:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,now true addiction
Dialogue: 0,1:49:20.80,1:49:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you're physiologically addicted
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.80,1:49:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and you stop the addiction
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.80,1:49:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the person will go into grand malconvulsions
Dialogue: 0,1:49:26.80,1:49:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and die
Dialogue: 0,1:49:28.80,1:49:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,so you're not dealing with just a fantasy
Dialogue: 0,1:49:30.80,1:49:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,you're also dealing with reality
Dialogue: 0,1:49:34.69,1:49:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the proven way
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.69,1:49:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,is via the 12 step program
Dialogue: 0,1:49:38.69,1:49:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and forgiveness comes about
Dialogue: 0,1:49:40.76,1:49:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,through inner honesty
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.76,1:49:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you're taking the steps
Dialogue: 0,1:49:44.76,1:49:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,doing the 3rd and the 4th and the 5th
Dialogue: 0,1:49:46.76,1:49:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and following that up with the 10th step
Dialogue: 0,1:49:57.94,1:50:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,all error comes out of ignorance
Dialogue: 0,1:50:00.58,1:50:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the teenage boy who starts to drink
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.58,1:50:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,for the excitement
Dialogue: 0,1:50:04.68,1:50:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the high being part of it
Dialogue: 0,1:50:06.68,1:50:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,being socially acceptable
Dialogue: 0,1:50:08.68,1:50:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's valued it's cool
Dialogue: 0,1:50:10.68,1:50:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,your old fraternity does it
Dialogue: 0,1:50:12.68,1:50:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea he was playing with fire
Dialogue: 0,1:50:14.80,1:50:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,he doesn't realize it until he's hooked
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.32,1:50:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that's why I say don't play with the devil
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.32,1:50:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,because he's been at it
Dialogue: 0,1:50:21.32,1:50:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,longer than you've been alive
Dialogue: 0,1:50:23.48,1:50:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and the built in temptations
Dialogue: 0,1:50:25.48,1:50:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,are seductive
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.15,1:50:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's too late by the time the person discovers that
Dialogue: 0,1:50:30.15,1:50:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,so forgive them
Dialogue: 0,1:50:32.15,1:50:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,for they know not what they do
Dialogue: 0,1:50:34.15,1:50:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,if you said to somebody at 15
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.15,1:50:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,would you like to drink
Dialogue: 0,1:50:38.15,1:50:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and become a sick dependent alcoholic
Dialogue: 0,1:50:40.15,1:50:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and have grand malconvulsions
Dialogue: 0,1:50:42.15,1:50:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,if you quit they'd all say no
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.76,1:50:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,then you have congenital
Dialogue: 0,1:50:46.76,1:50:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and ethnic
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.76,1:50:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and cultural proclivity
Dialogue: 0,1:50:50.76,1:50:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the farther north
Dialogue: 0,1:50:53.08,1:50:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,your ancestors come from the north pole
Dialogue: 0,1:50:55.08,1:50:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the greater your chance of addiction to alcohol
Dialogue: 0,1:50:57.08,1:50:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,chances if you're
Dialogue: 0,1:50:59.65,1:51:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,from Alaska
Dialogue: 0,1:51:01.65,1:51:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Eskimo tribes
Dialogue: 0,1:51:03.65,1:51:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Native Americans that live near the north pole
Dialogue: 0,1:51:05.65,1:51:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the likelihood of drinking
Dialogue: 0,1:51:07.65,1:51:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and not becoming addicted
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.65,1:51:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,is practically zero
Dialogue: 0,1:51:12.52,1:51:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,on the other hand if your ancestors
Dialogue: 0,1:51:14.52,1:51:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,come from closer to the equator
Dialogue: 0,1:51:16.55,1:51:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the Mediterranean sea
Dialogue: 0,1:51:18.55,1:51:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the likelihood of addiction is much less
Dialogue: 0,1:51:20.55,1:51:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,you can be Italian
Dialogue: 0,1:51:22.55,1:51:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and drink wine every day of your life
Dialogue: 0,1:51:24.55,1:51:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,so addiction
Dialogue: 0,1:51:27.06,1:51:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,seems to be related to latitude
Dialogue: 0,1:51:29.06,1:51:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and longitude
Dialogue: 0,1:51:31.06,1:51:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever it is
Dialogue: 0,1:51:33.06,1:51:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,North Pole-ism
Dialogue: 0,1:51:35.06,1:51:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I call it North Pole-ism
Dialogue: 0,1:51:37.06,1:51:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,so North Pole-ism
Dialogue: 0,1:51:39.06,1:51:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,1:51:41.06,1:51:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,if your grandparents
Dialogue: 0,1:51:43.06,1:51:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,are of Irish extraction
Dialogue: 0,1:51:45.06,1:51:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you know right from the beginning
Dialogue: 0,1:51:49.06,1:51:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,in Iceland
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.75,1:51:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,in Iceland I used to
Dialogue: 0,1:51:55.75,1:51:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,treat a patient from Reykjavik
Dialogue: 0,1:51:57.75,1:51:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and he would fly over once a month
Dialogue: 0,1:51:59.75,1:52:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,to see me from Iceland
Dialogue: 0,1:52:01.75,1:52:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the addiction there was 50%
Dialogue: 0,1:52:03.91,1:52:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,50% of the population
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.91,1:52:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,is addicted to alcohol
Dialogue: 0,1:52:07.91,1:52:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,so they have an endemic
Dialogue: 0,1:52:10.23,1:52:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,genetic
Dialogue: 0,1:52:12.29,1:52:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,cultural
Dialogue: 0,1:52:14.29,1:52:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,so it seems to me
Dialogue: 0,1:52:16.29,1:52:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the government and the education system
Dialogue: 0,1:52:18.29,1:52:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,should make you aware of that
Dialogue: 0,1:52:20.29,1:52:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,that you are born to a certain
Dialogue: 0,1:52:22.29,1:52:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,genetic strain
Dialogue: 0,1:52:24.29,1:52:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,that these types of substances
Dialogue: 0,1:52:26.29,1:52:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,are dangerous for you
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.29,1:52:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.48,1:52:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you answered a question that I actually didn't ask
Dialogue: 0,1:52:32.48,1:52:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,ok thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:52:34.48,1:52:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,alright so
Dialogue: 0,1:52:38.40,1:52:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,we give thanks to the Lord
Dialogue: 0,1:52:40.40,1:52:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,for thy presence
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.40,1:52:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,for thy love
Dialogue: 0,1:52:44.50,1:52:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,for thy blessing
Dialogue: 0,1:52:46.50,1:52:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,in being here
Dialogue: 0,1:52:48.56,1:52:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,each and one of you who is here
Dialogue: 0,1:52:50.56,1:52:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,does thereby your presence bless me
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.56,1:52:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and thereby do we
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.56,1:52:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,bless each other
Dialogue: 0,1:52:56.56,1:52:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and dedicate our lives
Dialogue: 0,1:52:58.56,1:53:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,to God
Dialogue: 0,1:53:00.56,1:53:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,to the pursuit of the divine truth
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.56,1:53:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and we do that
Dialogue: 0,1:53:04.56,1:53:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,all together
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.56,1:53:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,we have come in together
Dialogue: 0,1:53:08.56,1:53:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and we tend
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.63,1:53:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,like swooping in birds
Dialogue: 0,1:53:12.63,1:53:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,coming in together
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.63,1:53:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,we are sort of a cultural unit
Dialogue: 0,1:53:16.63,1:53:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and what holds us together is sort of this alignment
Dialogue: 0,1:53:18.63,1:53:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and although
Dialogue: 0,1:53:21.04,1:53:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,by the arm we got today
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.04,1:53:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,we are going to lose a few
Dialogue: 0,1:53:27.12,1:53:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,they can sign up for other venues
Dialogue: 0,1:53:29.38,1:53:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but
Dialogue: 0,1:53:31.38,1:53:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the propensity of this group is to spread out
Dialogue: 0,1:53:33.38,1:53:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,over time
Dialogue: 0,1:53:35.38,1:53:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,over great eons of time
Dialogue: 0,1:53:37.38,1:53:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and spread the truth of God throughout
Dialogue: 0,1:53:39.38,1:53:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole world
Dialogue: 0,1:53:59.46,1:54:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen
Dialogue: 0,1:54:08.15,1:54:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,ok wonderful
